00:26:03,420 --> 00:26:04,280
 sa 20 godina,

662
00:26:04,280 --> 00:26:04,980
 s 22 godina,

663
00:26:04,980 --> 00:26:05,620
 s 25 godina

664
00:26:05,620 --> 00:26:06,300
