00:26:06,300 --> 00:26:07,540
 Dakle, ti si imao 22

666
00:26:07,540 --> 00:26:08,760
 najstarije u Turbovodu

667
00:26:08,760 --> 00:26:09,480
 imao 20 godina.

668
00:26:09,480 --> 00:26:10,200
 25, da.

