 I misle da su Jugosloveni.

696
00:26:56,360 --> 00:26:57,260
 Takih je više.

697
00:26:57,260 --> 00:26:59,440
 Imao sam sve, imao sam,

698
00:26:59,440 --> 00:27:01,000
