00:27:16,360 --> 00:27:17,360
 Poduzetan si bio.

711
00:27:17,360 --> 00:27:18,180
 Poduzetan smo bili.

712
00:27:18,180 --> 00:27:20,640
 Taj dečko, taj moj prijatelj,

713
00:27:20,640 --> 00:27:21,220
 Goran Malinović,

714
00:27:21,220 --> 00:27:22,500
 je danas sto poslati invalid.

715
00:27:22,500 --> 00:27:24,620
 Živi na Borovju.

716
00:27:24,620 --> 00:27:26,840
 Sto poslati invalid.

717
00:27:26,840 --> 00:27:28,660
 Ten ga je pogodio 15.9.

718
00:27:28,660 --> 00:27:35,800
 Zabio mu je temelj kamenje u mozak.

