00:27:42,240 --> 00:27:43,700
 Sto poslati invalid.

724
00:27:43,700 --> 00:27:45,020
 Znači, a mogli smo to sve,

725
00:27:45,100 --> 00:27:46,300
 Filipa uzeti, otići u Zagreb,

726
00:27:46,300 --> 00:27:46,860
 otići na mora,

727
00:27:46,860 --> 00:27:47,620
 otići u Njemačku,

728
00:27:47,620 --> 00:27:49,020
 otići bilo gdje drugdje

729
00:27:49,020 --> 00:27:49,980
 i da me se uopće...

730
00:27:49,980 --> 00:27:51,220
 Ali ste odabrali ostati.

731
00:27:51,220 --> 00:27:52,260
 Odabrali smo ostati

732
00:27:52,260 --> 00:27:53,560
 za dobrobit ljudi

733
00:27:53,560 --> 00:27:54,640
 i za dobrobit naroda.

734
00:27:54,640 --> 00:27:55,960
 I zato, kažem,

735
00:27:55,960 --> 00:27:57,260
 ne mogu razumjeti politiku.

736
00:27:57,260 --> 00:27:59,080
 Niko ti ne zamjera...

737
00:27:59,080 --> 00:27:59,980
 Ušao si sad u nju,

738
00:27:59,980 --> 00:28:01,380
 ali i dalje ne razumijete.

739
00:28:01,380 --> 00:28:01,960
 Ne razumijem.

740
00:28:01,960 --> 00:28:02,860
 Ne mogu ja to razumijet.

741
00:28:02,860 --> 00:28:04,040
 I nikad neću razumijet.

742
