 Nikad moj glas više čut neće.

753
00:28:22,740 --> 00:28:23,520
 Ti si to rekao.

754
00:28:23,520 --> 00:28:24,800
 I da si ušao u sabor

755
00:28:24,800 --> 00:28:25,560
 da ih natiraš pronaći...

756
00:28:25,560 --> 00:28:26,620
 Samo to.

757
00:28:26,620 --> 00:28:27,840
 Nekih nađu,

758
00:28:27,840 --> 00:28:29,280
