00:29:26,180 --> 00:29:27,120
 da bi spašao ljude

801
00:29:27,120 --> 00:29:29,260
 koje ne poznaje civile.

802
00:29:29,260 --> 00:29:31,020
 Dakle, sada istovremeno

803
00:29:31,020 --> 00:29:32,720
 si na odboru za veterane

804
00:29:32,720 --> 00:29:33,380
 saborskom

805
00:29:33,380 --> 00:29:35,920
 glasao protiv njega.

806
00:29:36,120 --> 00:29:38,080
 mislim da je još

807
00:29:38,080 --> 00:29:39,420
 gospodin Bulj

808
00:29:39,420 --> 00:29:40,220
 glasao protiv

809
00:29:40,220 --> 00:29:41,640
 i gospodin Sačić.

810
00:29:41,640 --> 00:29:43,220
 Dakle, vas trojica ste glasili protiv.

811
00:29:43,220 --> 00:29:45,540
 HDZ je...

812
00:29:45,540 --> 00:29:46,420
 Imaju većinu.

813
00:29:46,420 --> 00:29:47,580
 Imaju većinu, tako.

814
00:29:47,580 --> 00:29:48,960
 Ida zakon u saborskom.

