 Ako se sad zakon

827
00:30:04,300 --> 00:30:04,880
 2021.

828
00:30:04,880 --> 00:30:06,360
 Kako Plenković voli reći,

829
00:30:06,360 --> 00:30:07,440
 pa 2020. godine

