00:30:08,240 --> 00:30:08,980
 docirat ljudima.

832
00:30:08,980 --> 00:30:10,200
 Ako 2021.

833
00:30:10,200 --> 00:30:11,460
 Željka,

834
00:30:11,460 --> 00:30:12,400
 mi radimo zakon

835
00:30:12,400 --> 00:30:14,220
