00:30:18,660 --> 00:30:20,060
 su nevina djeca stradala

840
00:30:20,060 --> 00:30:20,740
 1991. godine.

841
00:30:20,740 --> 00:30:21,780
 Ako mi radimo zakon

842
00:30:21,780 --> 00:30:22,580
 radi te djece,

843
00:30:22,580 --> 00:30:23,440
 to je sramota,

844
00:30:23,440 --> 00:30:24,920
 države ove

845
00:30:24,920 --> 00:30:26,280
 do neba je sramota.

846
00:30:26,280 --> 00:30:27,660
 Znači, ne radi se zakon

847
00:30:27,660 --> 00:30:28,440
 za te djecu.

848
00:30:28,440 --> 00:30:29,640
 Za tu djecu je napravljen

849
00:30:29,640 --> 00:30:30,040
