850
00:30:30,040 --> 00:30:31,200
 1992. kada je napravljen

851
00:30:31,200 --> 00:30:33,140
 zakon o ratnim vojnim invalidima,

852
00:30:33,140 --> 00:30:33,640
 napravljen odmah

853
00:30:33,640 --> 00:30:35,020
 i za civilne žrtve rata

854
00:30:35,020 --> 00:30:36,700
 i dosta je ljudi,

855
00:30:36,700 --> 00:30:37,460
 civila,

856
00:30:37,460 --> 00:30:38,660
 hrvatski civila

857
00:30:38,660 --> 00:30:39,300
 koji su stradali

858
00:30:39,300 --> 00:30:40,360
 od četničkih grata.

859
00:30:40,360 --> 00:30:41,180
 Četničkih napada.

860
00:30:41,180 --> 00:30:43,180
 Da, i po gradojima

861
00:30:43,180 --> 00:30:44,420
 snajkera, da.

862
00:30:44,420 --> 00:30:45,600
 Da, ni krivi, ni dužni.

863
00:30:45,600 --> 00:30:47,180
 Oni su ostvarili po tome.

864
00:30:47,180 --> 00:30:48,200
 Vjerovatno,

865
00:30:48,200 --> 00:30:48,860
 jedan će dio

866
00:30:48,860 --> 00:30:49,500
