867
00:30:49,500 --> 00:30:50,820
 ostvariti sada

868
00:30:50,820 --> 00:30:52,220
 pravo po ovome zakonu,

869
00:30:52,220 --> 00:30:53,480
 ali najveći broj će

870
00:30:53,480 --> 00:30:54,360
 Srba ostvariti.

871
00:30:54,360 --> 00:30:56,200
 Ali na koji način da?

872
00:30:56,200 --> 00:30:56,980
 Sašte rešite?

873
00:30:56,980 --> 00:30:58,120
 Oni su to jako,

874
00:30:58,120 --> 00:30:58,960
 jako dobro.

875
00:30:58,960 --> 00:30:59,800
 Oni su znali

876
00:30:59,800 --> 00:31:00,400
