 Iz kojeg razloga?

881
00:31:04,680 --> 00:31:05,500
 Jer tu ih razotkriva

882
00:31:05,500 --> 00:31:07,020
 golit i do kraja.

883
00:31:07,020 --> 00:31:08,240
 I onda je to,

884
00:31:08,360 --> 00:31:09,020
 opet Plenković,

885
00:31:09,020 --> 00:31:09,240
 to kaže,

886
00:31:09,240 --> 00:31:10,280
 uvijek ima nekog svoga

887
00:31:10,280 --> 00:31:11,700
