888
00:31:11,700 --> 00:31:13,180
 Branitelja kao smokvin list.

889
00:31:13,180 --> 00:31:14,460
 Znači, ima Tomu Medveda,

890
00:31:14,460 --> 00:31:15,220
 ima ovu

891
00:31:15,220 --> 00:31:17,160
