892
00:31:17,160 --> 00:31:18,360
 Da, iz Vukovara.

893
00:31:18,360 --> 00:31:20,060
 Sad se ne mogu sjeti

894
00:31:20,060 --> 00:31:20,640
 kako se zove.

895
00:31:20,640 --> 00:31:20,940
 Balić,

896
00:31:20,940 --> 00:31:22,180
 kolegica Balić.

897
00:31:22,180 --> 00:31:22,860
 Kolegica Balić,

898
00:31:22,860 --> 00:31:23,920
 koja je izgubila

899
00:31:23,920 --> 00:31:25,120
 oca i majku,

900
00:31:25,120 --> 00:31:26,480
 deset godina imao

901
