902
00:31:27,280 --> 00:31:28,360
 a koju Plenković

903
00:31:28,360 --> 00:31:28,980
 onda šalje

904
00:31:28,980 --> 00:31:29,860
 na tebe.

905
00:31:29,860 --> 00:31:30,460
 Da, da.

906
00:31:30,460 --> 00:31:31,480
 Da se vas dvoje

907
00:31:31,480 --> 00:31:32,120
 sukobljavati.

908
00:31:32,120 --> 00:31:32,960
 To mi je toliko,

909
00:31:33,480 --> 00:31:34,300
 to je doista

910
00:31:34,300 --> 00:31:36,320
 žalosno gledati.

911
00:31:36,320 --> 00:31:36,840
 Da, ali ja sam to bio

912
00:31:36,840 --> 00:31:37,260
 džentelmen,

913
00:31:37,260 --> 00:31:37,840
 neću jedan to.

914
00:31:37,840 --> 00:31:39,880
 Nikad ja postivam uvijek

915
00:31:39,880 --> 00:31:42,340
