00:31:42,340 --> 00:31:43,440
 dali su život za Hrvatsko,

917
00:31:43,440 --> 00:31:44,540
 to je za mene svetinja.

918
00:31:44,540 --> 00:31:46,580
 Politički se mi ne moramo slagati,

919
00:31:46,580 --> 00:31:47,320
 nećemo se slagati

920
00:31:47,320 --> 00:31:48,240
 dogodje ono u HDZ-u,

921
00:31:48,240 --> 00:31:49,520
 se nećemo slagati,

922
00:31:49,520 --> 00:31:50,100
 ali to je tako.

923
00:31:50,100 --> 00:31:51,240
 Ali za ovaj zakon

924
00:31:51,240 --> 00:31:52,140
 civilnih žrtomarata

925
00:31:52,140 --> 00:31:53,640
 to je najveća prevara koji su.

926
00:31:53,640 --> 00:31:54,280
 Oni su stavili

927
00:31:54,280 --> 00:31:55,640
 malte nevo na početak zakona.

928
00:31:55,640 --> 00:31:57,460
 Ne može ostvarniti pravo

929
00:31:57,460 --> 00:31:58,520
 ko je se borio

930
00:31:58,520 --> 00:32:00,020
 u neprijateljskim jedinicama

931
00:32:00,020 --> 00:32:00,680
 ovo, ono.

932
00:32:00,680 --> 00:32:01,600
 Oni su to sve nakitili.

933
00:32:01,600 --> 00:32:02,940
 Kad čovjek pročita,

934
00:32:02,940 --> 00:32:03,560
 vjeruj mi,

935
00:32:03,560 --> 00:32:05,340
 svako bi ga potpisao.

936
00:32:05,340 --> 00:32:07,020
 Ali moje prvo pitanje,

937
00:32:07,020 --> 00:32:07,600
 odmah sam se javio

938
00:32:07,600 --> 00:32:08,260
 prvi za riječ

939
00:32:08,260 --> 00:32:09,320
 kad je bilo na odboru,

940
00:32:09,320 --> 00:32:11,000
 kad je iz ministarstva je bio,

941
00:32:11,000 --> 00:32:12,100
 njih dvoje su došli

942
00:32:12,100 --> 00:32:13,640
 Nekić i Akmađa.

943
00:32:13,640 --> 00:32:15,440
 Ja sam samo pitao

944
00:32:15,440 --> 00:32:16,700
 kad sam mi to sve lijepo,

945
00:32:16,700 --> 00:32:17,900
 kada mi je isprezentirali

946
00:32:17,900 --> 00:32:18,540
 da bi čuo kreko,

947
00:32:18,540 --> 00:32:19,540
 pa ne sve biti proti toga.

948
00:32:19,540 --> 00:32:20,380
 Kako će biti proti toga

949
00:32:20,380 --> 00:32:21,700
 da civili naši,

950
00:32:22,140 --> 00:32:23,200
 i ako u meni odmah radi,

951
00:32:23,200 --> 00:32:24,500
 pa kako 2021. godine

952
00:32:24,500 --> 00:32:25,560
 mi rješavamo hrvatski civil

953
00:32:25,560 --> 00:32:26,200
 ako nismo rješili

954
00:32:26,200 --> 00:32:27,160
 do sada to nešto ne valja.

955
00:32:27,160 --> 00:32:28,600
 Onda ne valja vlast,

956
00:32:28,600 --> 00:32:29,560
 nije valjala 30 godina,

957
00:32:29,560 --> 00:32:30,700
 ko što i ne valja.

958
00:32:30,700 --> 00:32:31,460
 Ili da valja,

959
00:32:31,460 --> 00:32:32,600
 ne bi oni nestali ni ničega.

960
00:32:32,600 --> 00:32:34,880
 Ali moje prvo pitanje

961
00:32:34,880 --> 00:32:35,540
 njemu bilo,

962
00:32:35,540 --> 00:32:37,200
 oprostite gospodine,

963
00:32:37,200 --> 00:32:38,980
 jel vi imate popis agresora?

964
00:32:38,980 --> 00:32:40,040
 Jel vi imate popis

965
00:32:40,040 --> 00:32:41,320
 oni koji se borili protiv nas?

966
00:32:41,320 --> 00:32:42,840
 On je počeo mucat,

967
00:32:42,840 --> 00:32:44,040
 počeo, pa nemamo mit,

968
00:32:44,040 --> 00:32:44,820
 pa opaj,

969
00:32:44,820 --> 00:32:46,280
 nekaj ima bila koja institucija?

970
00:32:46,400 --> 00:32:47,060
 Jel ima sova?

971
00:32:47,060 --> 00:32:47,720
 Jel ima...

972
00:32:47,720 --> 00:32:49,120
 Jel netko u Hrvatskoj

973
00:32:49,120 --> 00:32:50,500
 ima popis ljudi

974
00:32:50,500 --> 00:32:52,340
 koji ne mogu koristi taj zakon?

975
00:32:52,340 --> 00:32:53,100
 On kaže, nemamo.

976
00:32:53,100 --> 00:32:54,440
 Pa kako će mi znati?

977
00:32:54,440 --> 00:32:56,000
 Znači, i ovo iz Borosela se prijaviti

978
00:32:56,000 --> 00:32:57,900
 ili bilo ko Savo iz Negoslavacije

979
00:32:57,900 --> 00:32:58,560
 ostvariće pravo

980
00:32:58,560 --> 00:32:59,740
 kad ti nemaš popis da vam tu.

981
00:32:59,740 --> 00:33:01,600
 Pa to će ministrat pod aktima.

982
00:33:01,600 --> 00:33:02,760
 Kakvim pod aktima?

983
00:33:02,760 --> 00:33:03,940
 Kakvim pod aktima?

984
00:33:03,940 --> 00:33:05,640
 Prijatelj, sam te pitan,

985
00:33:05,640 --> 00:33:08,120
 jel imate popis kompletno ovoga?

986
00:33:08,120 --> 00:33:09,000
 Nemate.

987
00:33:09,000 --> 00:33:10,980
 Bio je na tom odboru,

988
00:33:10,980 --> 00:33:12,960
 je bila treća točka dnevnog reda,

989
00:33:13,060 --> 00:33:15,920
 bilo je i izvješće nazora

990
00:33:15,920 --> 00:33:18,800
 za institutu domovinskog raza.

991
00:33:18,800 --> 00:33:20,980
 Bio je tu i nazor

992
00:33:20,980 --> 00:33:22,200
 i kasnije ga smo malo pričali sa njim.

993
00:33:22,200 --> 00:33:23,960
 Srbiji su javno imaju

994
00:33:23,960 --> 00:33:24,920
 na krajinskim televizijama

995
00:33:24,920 --> 00:33:25,740
 na knjinu koju danas

996
00:33:25,740 --> 00:33:26,440
 s njim se mogu naći.

997
00:33:26,440 --> 00:33:27,500
 Oni su imali žensku

998
00:33:27,500 --> 00:33:28,640
 minobacačku posadu

999
00:33:28,640 --> 00:33:29,500
 negdje kod Gospića.

1000
00:33:29,500 --> 00:33:33,260
 Imali su ženski interventni vod.

1001
00:33:33,260 --> 00:33:34,960
 Ja drugo govorim

1002
00:33:34,960 --> 00:33:35,840
 iz prve ruke

1003
00:33:35,840 --> 00:33:38,320
 nema civila u Boru, u selu

1004
00:33:38,320 --> 00:33:39,760
 u Negoslavacima 1991. godina.

1005
00:33:39,760 --> 00:33:40,500
 Nema civila.

1006
00:33:40,500 --> 00:33:41,900
 One žene koje su ostale,

1007
00:33:42,480 --> 00:33:43,720
 jer on je sjećaš što ti želi.

1008
00:33:43,720 --> 00:33:45,260
 On je igroka za bježanje

1009
00:33:45,260 --> 00:33:45,840
 preko Dunava,

1010
00:33:45,840 --> 00:33:46,700
 djece, vožnje,

1011
00:33:46,700 --> 00:33:48,060
 preboženje.

1012
00:33:48,060 --> 00:33:48,700
 Propagande srpske.

1013
00:33:48,700 --> 00:33:49,660
 Propagande da bi uplašili

1014
00:33:49,660 --> 00:33:51,060
 da bi kao zbjegovi

1015
00:33:51,060 --> 00:33:52,040
 bježe djeca, žene.

1016
00:33:52,040 --> 00:33:53,220
 Znači oni su svoju ženu

1017
00:33:53,220 --> 00:33:53,720
 i djecu odveli

1018
00:33:53,720 --> 00:33:54,480
 od kraja 1990.

1019
00:33:54,480 --> 00:33:55,660
 početak 1991. godine.

1020
00:33:55,660 --> 00:33:57,260
 Znači tamo više civila nema.

1021
00:33:57,260 --> 00:33:58,100
 To je ratna zona.

1022
00:33:58,100 --> 00:33:58,820
 Rat je bio

1023
00:33:58,820 --> 00:34:00,080
 sa njihove strane

1024
00:34:00,080 --> 00:34:00,700
 civila nema.

1025
00:34:00,700 --> 00:34:01,340
 Oni su odveli u...

1026
00:34:01,340 --> 00:34:02,700
 One žene koje su ostale

1027
00:34:02,700 --> 00:34:04,300
 su bile u njihovom sanitetu

1028
00:34:04,300 --> 00:34:05,220
 i su ih prebijali

1029
00:34:05,220 --> 00:34:06,240
 ili su im kuhali.

1030
00:34:06,240 --> 00:34:08,040
 Dakle, dio vojnih postrojba

1031
00:34:08,040 --> 00:34:08,920
 i dio vojnih postrojba

1032
00:34:08,920 --> 00:34:10,220
 i pa ćemo mi te...

1033
00:34:10,220 --> 00:34:10,840
 A na kraju,

1034
00:34:10,840 --> 00:34:11,680
 ključ svega,

1035
00:34:11,680 --> 00:34:13,480
 civili srbi

1036
00:34:13,480 --> 00:34:14,120
 koji su bili

1037
00:34:14,120 --> 00:34:14,980
 cijelo vrijeme

1038
00:34:14,980 --> 00:34:16,980
 okupacije

1039
00:34:16,980 --> 00:34:17,920
 srpske

1040
00:34:17,920 --> 00:34:19,020
 na našem teritoru

1041
00:34:19,020 --> 00:34:19,980
 koji su mi kontrolirali

1042
00:34:19,980 --> 00:34:20,480
 u Vukoru,

1043
00:34:20,480 --> 00:34:22,220
 taj mali dio grada

1044
00:34:22,220 --> 00:34:23,140
 koji smo kontrolirali,

1045
00:34:23,140 --> 00:34:24,260
 koji smo branili

1046
00:34:24,260 --> 00:34:24,840
 i to krvavo

1047
00:34:24,840 --> 00:34:25,880
 i dobro smo ga branili.

1048
00:34:27,520 --> 00:34:28,960
 Kad su izašli iz podruma,

1049
00:34:28,960 --> 00:34:30,780
 izašli su sa veknama kruha.

1050
00:34:30,780 --> 00:34:32,320
 Evo, ja sad kažem

1051
00:34:32,320 --> 00:34:33,600
 mi iz turbo voda

1052
00:34:33,600 --> 00:34:35,520
 zadnjih jedno 20 dana,

1053
00:34:35,520 --> 00:34:37,440
 15 se kladim u glavu.

1054
00:34:37,440 --> 00:34:39,020
 Nisam vidio kako kruha izgleda.

1055
00:34:39,020 --> 00:34:40,440
 Znači, nismo kruha jeli.

1056
00:34:40,440 --> 00:34:41,460
 Civili su.

1057
00:34:41,460 --> 00:34:42,520
 I ona ima snimka

1058
00:34:42,520 --> 00:34:43,720
 znači na Beograskoj televiziji.

1059
00:34:43,720 --> 00:34:44,620
 Žena izlazi van

1060
00:34:44,620 --> 00:34:45,720
 i više ja sam srpkinja.

1061
00:34:45,720 --> 00:34:48,020
 Evo, i sad jedem danas kruh

1062
00:34:48,020 --> 00:34:49,340
 i vadi kruh na snimci.

1063
00:34:49,340 --> 00:34:52,360
 Kad sam vidio to na YouTube

1064
00:34:52,360 --> 00:34:53,500
 meni je to ostalo osjećanje.

1065
00:34:53,500 --> 00:34:55,560
 To što ona jede kruh,

1066
00:34:55,560 --> 00:34:56,520
 ja blagosljivam.

1067
00:34:56,520 --> 00:34:57,880
 Ja s tim problema nemam.

1068
00:34:57,880 --> 00:34:58,980
 Što ga ja nisam jela.

1069
00:34:58,980 --> 00:34:59,640
 Ona je jela.

1070
00:34:59,640 --> 00:35:00,560
 I treba neke jela.

1071
00:35:00,560 --> 00:35:01,700
 Ona je civila, ona je žena.

1072
00:35:01,700 --> 00:35:03,540
 Ja tu starija.

1073
00:35:03,540 --> 00:35:04,200
 Ili nebitno.

1074
00:35:04,200 --> 00:35:05,600
 Ali ta žena

1075
00:35:05,600 --> 00:35:06,900
 nabraja u kameru

1076
00:35:06,900 --> 00:35:08,520
 braća ova, braća

1077
00:35:08,520 --> 00:35:09,440
 ona sada ne bi pogriješio

1078
00:35:09,440 --> 00:35:10,440
 koga neću namjeru imena

1079
00:35:10,440 --> 00:35:11,480
 jako znam dosta imena.

1080
00:35:11,480 --> 00:35:12,880
 Tih ljudi...

1081
00:35:12,880 --> 00:35:13,620
 Kako nabrala imena

1082
00:35:13,620 --> 00:35:14,360
 hrvatskih branitelja?

1083
00:35:14,360 --> 00:35:15,380
 Hrvatskih branitelja

1084
00:35:15,380 --> 00:35:17,060
 koji su je donosili unuta.

1085
00:35:17,060 --> 00:35:17,880
 Zato ih pozna.

1086
00:35:17,880 --> 00:35:19,680
 Koji su im donosili hranu.

1087
00:35:19,680 --> 00:35:21,160
 Ona ih nabroji.

1088
00:35:25,560 --> 00:35:26,840
 danas nisnaže.

1089
00:35:26,840 --> 00:35:28,280
 Da, ubili su ih.

1090
00:35:28,280 --> 00:35:29,720
 I jel ta žena sad

1091
00:35:29,720 --> 00:35:30,400
 ako se prijavi?

1092
00:35:30,400 --> 00:35:31,360
 Treba dobivati.

1093
00:35:31,360 --> 00:35:32,160
 Jel ona treba dobivati?

1094
00:35:32,160 --> 00:35:33,080
 Treba tvoje djete,

1095
00:35:33,080 --> 00:35:33,700
 moje djete

1096
00:35:33,700 --> 00:35:34,940
 i djeca koje imaju

1097
00:35:34,940 --> 00:35:35,440
 sad 10 godina.

1098
00:35:35,440 --> 00:35:36,140
 Zarađiva za nju novac.

1099
00:35:36,140 --> 00:35:36,940
 Zarađiva za nju.

1100
00:35:36,940 --> 00:35:37,660
 Slažim se.

1101
00:35:37,660 --> 00:35:38,440
 Pa ona je napravila,

1102
00:35:38,440 --> 00:35:39,340
 zapomeni, veće zlo

1103
00:35:39,340 --> 00:35:40,100
 nego nešto je puc.

1104
00:35:40,100 --> 00:35:41,500
 Ali, dobro,

1105
00:35:41,500 --> 00:35:43,180
 šta je zakon,

1106
00:35:43,180 --> 00:35:44,160
 taj predlog zakona

1107
00:35:44,160 --> 00:35:45,340
 je de facto,

1108
00:35:45,340 --> 00:35:46,440
 ako sam te dobro razumila,

1109
00:35:46,440 --> 00:35:47,840
 plot koalicije

1110
00:35:47,840 --> 00:35:49,300
 SDSS-a i HDZ-a.

1111
00:35:49,300 --> 00:35:49,580
 To je to.

1112
00:35:49,800 --> 00:35:51,400
 taj zakon je trebao još ići.

1113
00:35:51,400 --> 00:35:52,320
 Sjećam se.

1114
00:35:52,320 --> 00:35:53,800
 To je trebalo još ići za Glavašević.

1115
00:35:53,800 --> 00:35:56,360
 Da, ime Glavaševići ga je trebalo progurati,

1116
00:35:56,360 --> 00:35:57,880
 ali nije išlo.

1117
00:35:57,880 --> 00:35:59,820
 Dogodio se onaj prosvijet koji je to.

1118
00:35:59,820 --> 00:36:01,040
 Tako je, zaustavio, da.

1119
00:36:01,040 --> 00:36:02,980
 Ali danas nema prosvijeze,

1120
00:36:02,980 --> 00:36:03,540
 nema ničega.

1121
00:36:03,540 --> 00:36:04,880
 Taj zakon će isto ići.

1122
00:36:04,880 --> 00:36:06,020
 Isti će ljudi ostvariti

1123
00:36:06,020 --> 00:36:07,340
 koji tamo bila namjera.

1124
00:36:07,340 --> 00:36:08,800
 Ja sam vidio na kraju zakona,

1125
00:36:08,800 --> 00:36:09,840
 ti bi znaš bolje od mene,

1126
00:36:09,840 --> 00:36:10,740
 oko toga,

1127
00:36:10,740 --> 00:36:12,500
 kada je svaki zakon

1128
00:36:12,500 --> 00:36:13,360
 u javnoj raspravi

1129
00:36:13,360 --> 00:36:14,780
 da se može javiti bilo tko.

1130
00:36:14,780 --> 00:36:16,180
 Znate ko se javlja?

1131
00:36:16,180 --> 00:36:17,960
 Srpsko narodno viječe na kraju,

1132
00:36:17,960 --> 00:36:19,080
 Vesna Tešelić.

1133
00:36:19,080 --> 00:36:20,420
 Oni su zaintereseni za zakon

1134
00:36:20,420 --> 00:36:21,140
 u civilnim žrtama.

1135
00:36:21,140 --> 00:36:22,700
 Ne bih baš rekao da su za Hrvatske.

1136
00:36:22,700 --> 00:36:23,600
 Da se brinu da Hrvati dobiju.

1137
00:36:23,600 --> 00:36:24,340
 Da su ti koji su tamo,

1138
00:36:24,340 --> 00:36:25,640
 ja pročito ovog zakonu,

1139
00:36:25,640 --> 00:36:26,740
 da koji su bili,

1140
00:36:26,740 --> 00:36:29,260
 davali amadmane na pred,

1141
00:36:29,260 --> 00:36:31,680
 nego zaista da pravo ostvaruju.

1142
00:36:31,680 --> 00:36:32,820
 Pa tu ima svega željka.

1143
00:36:32,820 --> 00:36:35,160
 Od lječenja stipendija,

1144
00:36:35,160 --> 00:36:37,820
 od ovih toplica,

1145
00:36:37,820 --> 00:36:38,760
 od lječenja,

1146
00:36:38,760 --> 00:36:39,800
 od mirovina.

1147
00:36:39,960 --> 00:36:41,820
 Znači i to po većem koeficijentu

1148
00:36:41,820 --> 00:36:42,400
 se obračunalo

1149
00:36:42,400 --> 00:36:44,160
 nego što se braniteljima obračunalo.

1150
00:36:44,160 --> 00:36:45,840
 Ali što je sa braniteljskim udrugama

1151
00:36:45,840 --> 00:36:46,980
 u ovom trenutku?

1152
00:36:46,980 --> 00:36:49,640
 Zašto pristaju na to?

1153
00:36:49,640 --> 00:36:51,920
 Ili neznanje.

1154
00:36:51,920 --> 00:36:52,680
 Neznanje.

1155
00:36:52,680 --> 00:36:52,980
 Dobre.

1156
00:36:52,980 --> 00:36:53,960
 Ili jedan dio neznanje.

1157
00:36:53,960 --> 00:36:55,920
 Nadamo se da je najviše toga.

1158
00:36:55,920 --> 00:36:56,900
 Nadamo se tome, a drugo kupovina.

1159
00:36:56,900 --> 00:36:58,060
 Potreba biti iskreni reći.

1160
00:36:58,060 --> 00:37:00,440
 Ako neko dobiva novce

1161
00:37:00,440 --> 00:37:01,120
 iz onoga,

1162
00:37:01,120 --> 00:37:03,080
 iz ministarstva branitelja,

1163
00:37:03,080 --> 00:37:06,600
 ako je Medved Široke kao ministar ruke

1164
00:37:06,600 --> 00:37:07,660
 prema tim udrugama,

1165
00:37:07,660 --> 00:37:08,440
 oni će šutiti.

1166
00:37:08,520 --> 00:37:09,100
 vrlo jednostavno.

1167
00:37:09,100 --> 00:37:10,620
 I on misli, to s mene ne tiče.

1168
00:37:10,620 --> 00:37:12,140
 Ne razumije da se to tiče svakoga.

1169
00:37:12,140 --> 00:37:12,920
 Svakoga se to tiče.

1170
00:37:12,920 --> 00:37:13,420
 Svakog.

1171
00:37:13,420 --> 00:37:14,380
 To tiče njegovog djeteta.

1172
00:37:14,380 --> 00:37:16,580
 On će raditi za te i plaćat će to.

1173
00:37:16,580 --> 00:37:18,740
 Ali mislim, ali taj paradoks toga

1174
00:37:18,740 --> 00:37:22,960
 da se danas, 2021. ide financirati

1175
00:37:22,960 --> 00:37:25,220
 one koji su stvorili ratne štete

1176
00:37:25,220 --> 00:37:26,960
 za koje Hrvatska nije dobila novac,

1177
00:37:26,960 --> 00:37:28,860
 nikakvo obištećenje.

1178
00:37:28,860 --> 00:37:30,520
 Da se sada njih na kraju obištećaju,

1179
00:37:30,520 --> 00:37:32,600
 to je doista nema tu...

1180
00:37:32,600 --> 00:37:34,000
 A ne bi palo Andreju Plenkoviću,

1181
00:37:34,000 --> 00:37:35,320
 napravim, takvom velikom diplomati,

1182
00:37:35,320 --> 00:37:37,620
 da traži ratnu štete u Srbiju za nas zlogore,

1183
00:37:37,620 --> 00:37:40,240
 koji smo prošli na desetke tisuća Hrvate,

1184
00:37:40,240 --> 00:37:41,180
 prošlo pa kao logora.

1185
00:37:41,180 --> 00:37:45,520
 I u Srbiji, u Logorima, tako i u Hrvatskoj,

1186
00:37:45,520 --> 00:37:48,060
 i u Crnoj gori, i u Bosni i Hercegovini

1187
00:37:48,060 --> 00:37:50,780
 su odvodili naše ljude na početku ratu

1188
00:37:50,780 --> 00:37:53,140
 da kaže, a morate plato što to,

1189
00:37:53,140 --> 00:37:54,220
 bili ste strana u ratu,

1190
00:37:54,220 --> 00:37:55,860
 ako niste bili u stranu u ratu,

1191
00:37:55,860 --> 00:37:57,680
 pa što je Mlinarić i tisuće druge

1192
00:37:57,680 --> 00:37:59,100
 radilo u Nišu, u Zatvoru,

1193
00:37:59,100 --> 00:38:00,540
 u Stajićevo i u Sremskoj Mitrovici.

1194
00:38:00,540 --> 00:38:02,260
 Na kraju krajeva postoji dokumenti

1195
00:38:02,260 --> 00:38:03,160
 Međunanog Crvenog križa

1196
00:38:03,160 --> 00:38:03,980
 koji su nas popisali,

1197
00:38:03,980 --> 00:38:05,180
 znači jedan kroz jedan.

1198
00:38:05,180 --> 00:38:06,940
 Ako niste bili strana u ratu,

1199
00:38:07,380 --> 00:38:09,240
 rekli ste, oni su to sve vadili,

1200
00:38:09,240 --> 00:38:11,060
 ili ja sam osjetio na svojoj kože

1201
00:38:11,060 --> 00:38:13,020
 ne samo ja i ti ljudi koji su bili po Logorima,

1202
00:38:13,020 --> 00:38:14,760
 što znači do priznanja Hrvatske

1203
00:38:14,760 --> 00:38:16,080
 i poslije priznanja.

1204
00:38:16,080 --> 00:38:18,440
 Do priznanja Hrvatske smo uvijekat

1205
00:38:18,440 --> 00:38:19,740
 pobunjenik taj, taj.

1206
00:38:19,740 --> 00:38:21,880
 Kad je Hrvatska priznata 15.1.1992,

1207
00:38:21,880 --> 00:38:23,020
 onda je bil tako zarubljenik.

1208
00:38:23,020 --> 00:38:26,100
 Znači mi smo po njima bili tada pobunjenici,

1209
00:38:26,100 --> 00:38:28,000
 ali ako smo poslije 15.1.

1210
00:38:28,000 --> 00:38:28,840
 kada je Hrvatska priznata

1211
00:38:28,840 --> 00:38:29,600
 što nisu otvorili vrata,

1212
00:38:29,600 --> 00:38:31,580
 rekli, idite, pustili vas tako doma.

1213
00:38:32,080 --> 00:38:33,140
 Znači nisu to napravili.

1214
00:38:33,140 --> 00:38:34,800
 Niko ne pita za naše oštete,

1215
00:38:34,800 --> 00:38:37,120
 a to su najugroženija skupina

1216
00:38:37,120 --> 00:38:39,040
 branitelja, su Logoraši.

1217
00:38:39,040 --> 00:38:41,320
 U prošijek u miru sa 53 godine.

1218
00:38:41,320 --> 00:38:41,840
 To sam sigurno.

1219
00:38:41,840 --> 00:38:43,900
 Da, s obzirom na muke koje ste preživili.

1220
00:38:43,900 --> 00:38:45,080
 I na stres i na sve.

1221
00:38:45,080 --> 00:38:47,480
 I na sve što ste pretrpjeli.

1222
00:38:47,480 --> 00:38:51,380
 Ali nekako, kako ti,

1223
00:38:51,380 --> 00:38:53,680
 ja uvijek me jako zasmeta

1224
00:38:53,680 --> 00:38:54,680
 kad čujem da netko kaže

1225
00:38:54,680 --> 00:38:55,700
 kakva je ovo država.

1226
00:38:55,700 --> 00:38:58,420
 Ovo je divna država.

1227
00:38:58,420 --> 00:39:02,260
 To isto kao da bi čovjek rekao

1228
00:39:02,260 --> 00:39:03,240
 za svoje djete kako je.

1229
00:39:03,240 --> 00:39:04,800
 Ne, država je fenomenalna.

1230
00:39:04,800 --> 00:39:06,240
 Bog je stvorio za nas Hrvata,

1231
00:39:06,240 --> 00:39:08,220
 ali vlast treba mijenjati.

1232
00:39:08,220 --> 00:39:09,920
 Točka, amen, nema gotovo.

1233
00:39:09,920 --> 00:39:12,140
 Država uvijek se mora voliti.

1234
00:39:12,140 --> 00:39:13,560
 Država je prekrasna

1235
00:39:13,560 --> 00:39:15,100
 od Slavonje ravne,

1236
00:39:15,100 --> 00:39:16,280
 od Brežuljaka,

1237
00:39:16,280 --> 00:39:17,280
 Zagorskih,

1238
00:39:17,280 --> 00:39:18,180
 od like,

1239
00:39:18,180 --> 00:39:19,840
 brdovite,

1240
00:39:19,840 --> 00:39:20,520
 planinske,

1241
00:39:20,520 --> 00:39:22,300
 do mora našeg Jadranskog prekrasnog.

1242
00:39:22,300 --> 00:39:24,140
 Nema ljepše države na svijetu za živjeti.

1243
00:39:24,140 --> 00:39:29,060
 Razina frustracije te

1244
00:39:29,060 --> 00:39:31,840
 među ljudima koji su ovakve žrtve podnijeli

1245
00:39:31,840 --> 00:39:33,340
 kao ti i kao mnogi drugi.

1246
00:39:33,340 --> 00:39:36,580
 Meni je uvijek kad su ovakve nekakve situacije

1247
00:39:36,580 --> 00:39:38,420
 kada se vrijeđa branitelje,

1248
00:39:38,420 --> 00:39:40,160
 kad se omalovažava domovinski rat,

1249
00:39:40,160 --> 00:39:41,660
 kad se laže ljudima u lice,

1250
00:39:41,660 --> 00:39:43,500
 ja se uvijek pitam kako je to onima

1251
00:39:43,500 --> 00:39:45,460
 koji su najveće žrtve dali.

1252
00:39:45,720 --> 00:39:47,200
 brata si ti svog dao,

1253
00:39:47,200 --> 00:39:47,780
 ne znam,

1254
00:39:47,780 --> 00:39:49,840
 moja tri brata su živa.

1255
00:39:49,840 --> 00:39:51,540
 Hoću reći,

1256
00:39:51,540 --> 00:39:53,740
 koliko je to teško

1257
00:39:53,740 --> 00:39:55,220
 izdržavati ljudima,

1258
00:39:55,220 --> 00:39:57,040
 samo ono što slušaju

1259
00:39:57,040 --> 00:40:00,080
 i što mediji kreiraju neistine,

1260
00:40:00,080 --> 00:40:01,040
 jedan dio medija.

1261
00:40:01,040 --> 00:40:03,140
 Ma, Željka, ja opraštam svima sve.

1262
00:40:03,140 --> 00:40:05,260
 I neprijateljima koji su me tukli,

1263
00:40:05,260 --> 00:40:06,480
 ja opraštam sve,

1264
00:40:06,480 --> 00:40:07,600
 apsolutno sve.

1265
00:40:07,600 --> 00:40:09,380
 Ne opraštam jedino

1266
00:40:09,380 --> 00:40:11,260
 političarima našima.

1267
00:40:11,260 --> 00:40:12,840
 Ja nisam očekivao

1268
00:40:12,840 --> 00:40:14,560
 od Šlivančina da će donet meni bombone,

1269
00:40:14,720 --> 00:40:15,360
 da sam ne razumijem.

1270
00:40:15,360 --> 00:40:16,700
 Ja sam od njega očekivao

1271
00:40:16,700 --> 00:40:17,240
 ono što je bilo.

1272
00:40:17,240 --> 00:40:18,560
 Pa niti od Stanimirovića

1273
00:40:18,560 --> 00:40:19,220
 nisi očekivao

1274
00:40:19,220 --> 00:40:20,260
 da se bori za Hrvatsku.

1275
00:40:20,260 --> 00:40:20,280
 Niti od Stanimirovića,

1276
00:40:20,280 --> 00:40:21,900
 niti očekavim od Pupu

1277
00:40:21,900 --> 00:40:22,840
 da se bori za ovo.

1278
00:40:22,840 --> 00:40:24,400
 Ali bom je od Plenkovića

1279
00:40:24,400 --> 00:40:24,920
 očekujem.

1280
00:40:24,920 --> 00:40:26,880
 Ali ne očekujem

1281
00:40:26,880 --> 00:40:28,160
 niti od Plenkovića

1282
00:40:28,160 --> 00:40:29,560
 da se bori više za mene.

1283
00:40:29,560 --> 00:40:31,400
 Ni da se bori

1284
00:40:31,400 --> 00:40:32,780
 za oštetu,

1285
00:40:32,780 --> 00:40:33,140
 logu,

1286
00:40:33,140 --> 00:40:34,000
 da mene novac.

1287
00:40:34,000 --> 00:40:35,100
 Evo, sad javno kažem,

1288
00:40:35,100 --> 00:40:35,780
 a rekao sam to još

1289
00:40:35,780 --> 00:40:36,580
 u jednoj emisiji.

1290
00:40:37,060 --> 00:40:37,860
 javno kažem,

1291
00:40:37,860 --> 00:40:39,080
 to je krvav novac.

1292
00:40:39,080 --> 00:40:40,360
 Krvavo sam ga batin

1293
00:40:40,360 --> 00:40:41,080
 da bi ga zaradilo

1294
00:40:41,080 --> 00:40:41,780
 to što bi Srblja

1295
00:40:41,780 --> 00:40:42,600
 trebala isplatiti.

1296
00:40:42,600 --> 00:40:43,480
 Ja ga poklanjam

1297
00:40:43,480 --> 00:40:44,340
 bolestnoj djeci.

1298
00:40:44,340 --> 00:40:46,380
 Prekrvavo sam ga zaradio

1299
00:40:46,380 --> 00:40:48,320
 da bi ga pre lagano potrošio.

1300
00:40:48,480 --> 00:40:50,220
 Znači, ja ga moram dat negdje

1301
00:40:50,220 --> 00:40:51,180
 gdje znam da će...

1302
00:40:51,180 --> 00:40:52,000
 Isto tako teško.

1303
00:40:52,000 --> 00:40:52,660
 Gdje je teško.

1304
00:40:52,660 --> 00:40:54,800
 Znači, mene to ne zanima novac.

1305
00:40:54,800 --> 00:40:57,540
 Mene zanima presuda za povijest.

1306
00:40:57,540 --> 00:40:59,260
 Jer nabijat će nam ove ustaše

1307
00:40:59,260 --> 00:41:00,360
 koje meni nabije

1308
00:41:00,360 --> 00:41:01,600
 koje sam ođa 69. godine

1309
00:41:01,600 --> 00:41:02,480
 ne mogu se oprati

1310
00:41:02,480 --> 00:41:03,140
 od toga nazivati.

1311
00:41:03,140 --> 00:41:05,300
 Naravno, i dalje će o tome pričat,

1312
00:41:05,300 --> 00:41:05,760
 lagat.

1313
00:41:05,760 --> 00:41:07,000
 Kao da je u Hrvatskoj

1314
00:41:07,000 --> 00:41:09,000
 postoji srpska propagandna mašina.

1315
00:41:09,000 --> 00:41:09,500
 Jasno, jasno.

1316
00:41:09,500 --> 00:41:11,720
 Evo, i zamjeram politici

1317
00:41:11,720 --> 00:41:13,180
 znači, krajem, opraštam sve.

1318
00:41:13,180 --> 00:41:15,080
 Rat, logor, ništa me to

1319
00:41:15,080 --> 00:41:16,340
 apsolutno sve oprašta.

1320
00:41:16,340 --> 00:41:18,360
 Ne opraštam im politici

1321
00:41:18,360 --> 00:41:20,000
 našoj odnos prema mladima

1322
00:41:20,000 --> 00:41:21,280
 da naši mladi moraju bježati

1323
00:41:21,280 --> 00:41:22,200
 iz ove pravljajpe države.

1324
00:41:22,200 --> 00:41:23,760
 To im ne moglo prosto nikako.

1325
00:41:23,760 --> 00:41:24,800
 Zato sam se uključio

1326
00:41:24,800 --> 00:41:25,660
 u ovu političku borbu

1327
00:41:25,660 --> 00:41:26,820
 i zato ću se boriti

1328
00:41:26,820 --> 00:41:28,240
 isto koji se borio u Vukovara.

1329
00:41:28,240 --> 00:41:30,160
 Bez kompromisa u kost,

1330
00:41:30,160 --> 00:41:31,960
 u glavu, stalno

1331
00:41:31,960 --> 00:41:33,160
 i bez kompromisa.

1332
00:41:33,160 --> 00:41:35,400
 I koje sad su koraci

1333
00:41:35,400 --> 00:41:36,420
 vezane za ovaj zakon

1334
00:41:36,420 --> 00:41:37,440
 o civilnim želitvama rata?

1335
00:41:37,540 --> 00:41:39,660
 Što je ono što se sad tu može napraviti

1336
00:41:39,660 --> 00:41:41,540
 da se spriječi Plenkovića

1337
00:41:41,540 --> 00:41:42,540
 da provede zakon

1338
00:41:42,540 --> 00:41:43,140
 koji je štetan

1339
00:41:43,140 --> 00:41:44,700
 na štetu Hrvatske?

1340
00:41:44,700 --> 00:41:46,640
 Ne možete vi tu napraviti ništa

1341
00:41:46,640 --> 00:41:47,680
 kao oporba.

1342
00:41:47,680 --> 00:41:48,860
 Ja sam siguran

1343
00:41:48,860 --> 00:41:50,140
 i u generala Sačića

1344
00:41:50,140 --> 00:41:52,120
 da će staviti amanumane.

1345
00:41:52,120 --> 00:41:53,800
 Ja ću staviti amanumane na zakon.

1346
00:41:53,800 --> 00:41:55,500
 Mirobulj, očitavno os će staviti.

1347
00:41:55,500 --> 00:41:56,420
 Mirobulj, obaveza će staviti.

1348
00:41:56,420 --> 00:41:57,340
 Mirobulj, obaveza će staviti.

1349
00:41:57,340 --> 00:41:58,060
 Nos spomenuo mi ja bulja svoga.

1350
00:41:58,060 --> 00:41:59,040
 Ja ga nevam.

1351
00:41:59,040 --> 00:42:00,700
 Mi tamo koj jedan

1352
00:42:00,700 --> 00:42:01,760
 kad nastupamo.

1353
00:42:02,240 --> 00:42:03,360
 Ali ja uopće ne samim

1354
00:42:03,360 --> 00:42:05,060
 u nastrojicu

1355
00:42:05,060 --> 00:42:05,920
 da ćemo pokušati

1356
00:42:05,920 --> 00:42:06,740
 da dopravamo sam

1357
00:42:06,740 --> 00:42:07,620
 ali nažalost

1358
00:42:07,620 --> 00:42:09,120
 oni imaju većinu

1359
00:42:09,120 --> 00:42:10,520
 Dobro, ali ima u HDZ-u

1360
00:42:10,520 --> 00:42:11,800
 branitelja ljudi

1361
00:42:11,800 --> 00:42:13,120
 koji su sisto s vama boreli

1362
00:42:13,120 --> 00:42:14,720
 pa treba i njih potaknuti

1363
00:42:14,720 --> 00:42:15,300
 da se i oni

1364
00:42:15,300 --> 00:42:17,060
 Sagnu glavu, rekao sam te.

1365
00:42:17,060 --> 00:42:17,300
 Sagnu glavu stedi.

1366
00:42:17,300 --> 00:42:17,880
 Možda neće.

1367
00:42:17,880 --> 00:42:18,720
 Ja moram lići.

1368
00:42:18,720 --> 00:42:20,200
 Ja se uvijek nadam

1369
00:42:20,200 --> 00:42:21,500
 da će ljudi...

1370
00:42:21,500 --> 00:42:22,720
 Znaš što će reći mi?

1371
00:42:22,720 --> 00:42:25,120
 Ti ljudi iz HDZ-a

1372
00:42:25,120 --> 00:42:25,840
 oni će reći

1373
00:42:25,840 --> 00:42:27,160
 vidiš da piše u zakonu

1374
00:42:27,160 --> 00:42:28,400
 da ne mogu nepreteljske...

1375
00:42:28,400 --> 00:42:29,440
 Ali nisu pobrojali.

1376
00:42:29,440 --> 00:42:31,900
 Ali to je najveća laž.

1377
00:42:31,900 --> 00:42:32,260
 To je isto

1378
00:42:32,260 --> 00:42:34,400
 ona koja je najveća vražija laž

1379
00:42:34,400 --> 00:42:35,520
 da ga nema, da ne postoji.

1380
00:42:35,520 --> 00:42:36,240
 E tako i ovo.

1381
00:42:36,240 --> 00:42:37,400
 Ti si tu stavio na papir.

1382
00:42:37,400 --> 00:42:38,340
 Jesi stavio.

1383
00:42:38,340 --> 00:42:39,500
 To lijepo stoji na papiru.

1384
00:42:39,500 --> 00:42:40,860
 Ali je neprovedivo.

1385
00:42:40,860 --> 00:42:42,540
 To provedivo ne možeš.

1386
00:42:42,540 --> 00:42:44,800
 Objavi javno popis

1387
00:42:44,800 --> 00:42:47,040
 ljudi koji se borili

1388
00:42:47,040 --> 00:42:47,640
 proti Hrvatske.

1389
00:42:47,640 --> 00:42:49,100
 Kako ste objavili popis branitelja?

1390
00:42:49,100 --> 00:42:50,120
 Što se mene tiče

1391
00:42:50,120 --> 00:42:50,880
 možda i danas objavio.

1392
00:42:50,880 --> 00:42:52,240
 Ja se nema ček stiditi.

1393
00:42:52,300 --> 00:42:53,340
 Ja sam svoju zemlju branio,

1394
00:42:53,340 --> 00:42:54,080
 svoju državu branio,

1395
00:42:54,080 --> 00:42:54,820
 svoj grad branio.

1396
00:42:54,820 --> 00:42:56,040
 To bi radio i danas.

1397
00:42:56,040 --> 00:42:57,860
 Dakle imamo objavljen javno

1398
00:42:57,860 --> 00:42:58,740
 popis branitelja,

1399
00:42:58,740 --> 00:43:00,320
 ne imamo javno objavljen

1400
00:43:00,320 --> 00:43:01,240
 popis napadača.

1401
00:43:01,240 --> 00:43:01,960
 Napadača, da.

1402
00:43:01,960 --> 00:43:03,040
 Pa mi nemamo,

1403
00:43:03,040 --> 00:43:04,700
 želj kako ćemo ići u...

1404
00:43:04,700 --> 00:43:05,140
 Ali kažem,

1405
00:43:05,140 --> 00:43:06,260
 razočaram se,

1406
00:43:06,260 --> 00:43:07,160
 opet kajem,

1407
00:43:07,160 --> 00:43:08,120
 ne u državu nego u vlast.

1408
00:43:08,120 --> 00:43:09,020
 Pa mi nemamo popis

1409
00:43:09,020 --> 00:43:09,480
 još poginjuli.

1410
00:43:09,480 --> 00:43:10,420
 Pa nama je fratar

1411
00:43:10,420 --> 00:43:12,060
 iz Vukovara napravio

1412
00:43:12,060 --> 00:43:14,020
 2717 ljudi koji su poginjuli.

1413
00:43:14,020 --> 00:43:15,320
 Vukovar država ga nimala popis.

1414
00:43:22,300 --> 00:43:23,780
 je u interesu Hrvatske.

1415
00:43:23,780 --> 00:43:26,060
 U interesu onog što je...

1416
00:43:26,060 --> 00:43:26,580
 U konačnici,

1417
00:43:26,580 --> 00:43:27,260
 ovo što ti govoriš,

1418
00:43:27,260 --> 00:43:28,520
 što je ekonomski važno.

1419
00:43:28,520 --> 00:43:30,640
 To su sve elementi

1420
00:43:30,640 --> 00:43:31,380
 o kojima govorimo

1421
00:43:31,380 --> 00:43:33,460
 i tužbe i odštete

1422
00:43:33,460 --> 00:43:35,260
 i ova plaćanja novca

1423
00:43:35,260 --> 00:43:36,420
 kojima se sad financira

1424
00:43:36,420 --> 00:43:37,140
 ova koalicija

1425
00:43:37,140 --> 00:43:38,280
 sa SDSS-om

1426
00:43:38,280 --> 00:43:39,700
 kroz različite zakone.

1427
00:43:39,700 --> 00:43:41,700
 To je sve bitno za Hrvatsku

1428
00:43:41,700 --> 00:43:42,900
 jer su to ekonomski

1429
00:43:42,900 --> 00:43:43,700
 ili tereti

1430
00:43:43,700 --> 00:43:45,180
 ili koristi za Hrvatsku.

1431
00:43:45,180 --> 00:43:46,900
 Ovo će biti veliki tereti.

1432
00:43:46,900 --> 00:43:48,460
 Ja sam vidio

1433
00:43:48,460 --> 00:43:49,360
 kako se proračun

1434
00:43:49,360 --> 00:43:50,640
 udvostručava

1435
00:43:50,640 --> 00:43:51,700
 u 2022-oj

1436
00:43:51,700 --> 00:43:53,140
 i u 2023-2024.

1437
00:43:53,140 --> 00:43:53,800
 predviđanja.

1438
00:43:53,800 --> 00:43:54,080
 Znači,

1439
00:43:54,080 --> 00:43:56,240
 do sad se karihiram

1440
00:43:56,240 --> 00:43:56,920
 100 miliona,

1441
00:43:56,920 --> 00:43:58,640
 u 2022-oj

1442
00:43:58,640 --> 00:43:59,600
 200 miliona.

1443
00:43:59,600 --> 00:43:59,960
 Znači,

1444
00:43:59,960 --> 00:44:00,960
 oni već znaju

1445
00:44:00,960 --> 00:44:01,920
 broj ljudi koji će

1446
00:44:01,920 --> 00:44:03,300
 vjerojatno dogovoreno...

1447
00:44:03,300 --> 00:44:03,560
 Dobro.

1448
00:44:03,560 --> 00:44:04,100
 I šta sad?

1449
00:44:04,100 --> 00:44:05,920
 Mi sad imamo državu

1450
00:44:05,920 --> 00:44:08,140
 za koju smo se izborili

1451
00:44:08,140 --> 00:44:09,480
 teškom mukom.

1452
00:44:09,480 --> 00:44:10,140
 Imamo ju.

1453
00:44:10,140 --> 00:44:11,360
 Imamo

1454
00:44:11,360 --> 00:44:13,040
 30 godina

1455
00:44:13,040 --> 00:44:14,040
 Hrvatska postoji.

1456
00:44:14,040 --> 00:44:14,560
 Mi,

1457
00:44:14,560 --> 00:44:15,140
 2021.

1458
00:44:15,140 --> 00:44:16,660
 stranka koja je tada

1459
00:44:16,660 --> 00:44:17,700
 branila Hrvatsku

1460
00:44:17,700 --> 00:44:18,800
 i pomagala

1461
00:44:18,800 --> 00:44:20,960
 i vodiju čovjek

1462
00:44:20,960 --> 00:44:21,660
 i vodiju ekipa

1463
00:44:21,660 --> 00:44:23,020
 koja ju iskoristava

1464
00:44:23,020 --> 00:44:24,220
 po sve mom sudeći.

1465
00:44:24,220 --> 00:44:25,200
 Dakle,

1466
00:44:25,200 --> 00:44:26,780
 što je ono što

1467
00:44:26,780 --> 00:44:28,200
 se može napraviti?

1468
00:44:28,200 --> 00:44:28,780
 Što je ono

1469
00:44:28,780 --> 00:44:30,360
 smjer u kojem ti vidiš

1470
00:44:30,360 --> 00:44:30,820
 svjetlo?

1471
00:44:30,820 --> 00:44:32,000
 Meni je to fascinantno

1472
00:44:32,000 --> 00:44:32,560
 kako si ti

1473
00:44:32,560 --> 00:44:33,800
 pun energije

1474
00:44:33,800 --> 00:44:34,200
 i kako

1475
00:44:34,200 --> 00:44:36,260
 ljubavi i nade

1476
00:44:36,260 --> 00:44:37,300
 i svega za Hrvatsku.

1477
00:44:37,300 --> 00:44:37,540
 Dakle,

1478
00:44:37,540 --> 00:44:40,260
 što će se dalje događati?

1479
00:44:40,560 --> 00:44:40,760
 Evo,

1480
00:44:40,760 --> 00:44:41,800
 ohrabri me malo.

1481
00:44:41,800 --> 00:44:42,600
 Hrabri me.

1482
00:44:42,600 --> 00:44:42,980
 Opet,

1483
00:44:42,980 --> 00:44:44,040
 ja ću se uvijek

1484
00:44:44,040 --> 00:44:44,880
 uvijek

1485
00:44:44,880 --> 00:44:46,200
 osanjati na mlade.

1486
00:44:46,200 --> 00:44:47,400
 Tu energiju,

1487
00:44:47,400 --> 00:44:47,780
 moju,

1488
00:44:47,780 --> 00:44:48,240
 tvoju,

1489
00:44:48,240 --> 00:44:49,100
 bilo čiju,

1490
00:44:49,100 --> 00:44:49,480
 naši,

1491
00:44:49,480 --> 00:44:49,780
 koju smo...

1492
00:44:49,780 --> 00:44:50,580
 Mi nismo više mladi.

1493
00:44:50,580 --> 00:44:51,680
 Ne, ne, ne, ne.

1494
00:44:51,680 --> 00:44:52,840
 Samo neke preuzme.

1495
00:44:52,840 --> 00:44:54,640
 I tu ljubav koju smo imali

1496
00:44:54,640 --> 00:44:55,580
 samo neke...

1497
00:44:55,580 --> 00:44:56,800
 Ma, 10% da pre...

1498
00:44:56,800 --> 00:44:57,480
 I koju imamo,

1499
00:44:57,480 --> 00:44:58,980
 10% samo da ih imaju.

1500
00:44:58,980 --> 00:45:00,300
 Mladi mogu sve.

1501
00:45:00,300 --> 00:45:01,960
 Samo se moraju hrabrit

1502
00:45:01,960 --> 00:45:03,140
 i krenuti.

1503
00:45:03,140 --> 00:45:04,100
 Mladi,

1504
00:45:04,100 --> 00:45:05,220
 školovani,

1505
00:45:05,220 --> 00:45:06,240
 obrazovani,

1506
00:45:06,240 --> 00:45:06,920
 lijepi,

1507
00:45:06,920 --> 00:45:07,640
 zdravi.

1508
00:45:07,640 --> 00:45:08,560
 Kad ih vidiš,

1509
00:45:08,560 --> 00:45:10,320
 oni mogu svijet mijenja.

1510
00:45:10,320 --> 00:45:12,280
 Samo moraju se upustiti.

1511
00:45:12,280 --> 00:45:13,720
 Ne smiju okretati glavu

1512
00:45:13,720 --> 00:45:15,540
 jer običajim se to glavu.

1513
00:45:15,540 --> 00:45:16,160
 Ne smiju.

1514
00:45:16,160 --> 00:45:16,340
 Sigurno.

1515
00:45:16,340 --> 00:45:19,280
 Treba ulaziti u borbe.

1516
00:45:19,280 --> 00:45:20,540
 Treba u borbu.

1517
00:45:20,540 --> 00:45:22,180
 U onu borbu koja je onda bila aktualna

1518
00:45:22,180 --> 00:45:23,500
 danas u druge neke borbe,

1519
00:45:23,500 --> 00:45:24,100
 danas...

1520
00:45:24,100 --> 00:45:26,120
 Evo sad ću joj sad opet nekajim

1521
00:45:26,120 --> 00:45:27,480
 kao flashback-ovi u glavi.

1522
00:45:27,480 --> 00:45:31,780
 Tenki je bio 30 metara od mjestne zajednice.

1523
00:45:31,780 --> 00:45:33,500
 Blago Zadro je stavio tamo

1524
00:45:33,500 --> 00:45:34,520
 gdje mu je sad bista tamo

1525
00:45:34,520 --> 00:45:35,100
 i ona mjestna zajednica.

1526
00:45:35,100 --> 00:45:36,100
 Ona je zidić malo.

1527
00:45:36,100 --> 00:45:37,820
 Nas je bilo jedno deset.

1528
00:45:37,820 --> 00:45:39,700
 Osam do deset mumaka iza njega.

1529
00:45:39,700 --> 00:45:41,560
 I on je...

1530
00:45:41,560 --> 00:45:43,040
 Znali smo Tenki ideje.

1531
00:45:43,040 --> 00:45:45,160
 Treba mu još jedno deset sekundi.

1532
00:45:45,160 --> 00:45:47,400
 Tresa se zemlja ispod svega

1533
00:45:47,400 --> 00:45:48,500
 koja je toga dosijelja,

1534
00:45:48,500 --> 00:45:49,660
 koja je to zvuk,

1535
00:45:49,820 --> 00:45:51,460
 pucnjava granate na sve strane.

1536
00:45:51,460 --> 00:45:52,520
 I on je rekao

1537
00:45:52,520 --> 00:45:54,060
 Dečki, izvadite bombe,

1538
00:45:54,060 --> 00:45:56,040
 nećemo se povući.

1539
00:45:56,040 --> 00:45:57,900
 Ako dođe, bacit će ručne bombe.

1540
00:45:57,900 --> 00:45:59,940
 Znači, ne može što Tenki počešat s tim.

1541
00:45:59,940 --> 00:46:02,900
 Znači, htio ti je zapravo reći,

1542
00:46:02,900 --> 00:46:03,500
 umrijet ćemo,

1543
00:46:03,500 --> 00:46:04,700
 ali se povuću odavde nećemo.

1544
00:46:05,240 --> 00:46:06,820
 Nitko željka nije otišo.

1545
00:46:06,820 --> 00:46:07,860
 O ti deset ljudi.

1546
00:46:07,860 --> 00:46:09,320
 Mogu se svako ukrenuti,

1547
00:46:09,320 --> 00:46:10,440
 otrčati, otići.

1548
00:46:10,440 --> 00:46:11,520
 Da, i nikomu ne bi zamijerio.

1549
00:46:11,520 --> 00:46:12,300
 Nikomu ne bi zamijerio,

1550
00:46:12,300 --> 00:46:13,520
 ne bi mi ni blago zamijerio.

1551
00:46:13,520 --> 00:46:14,940
 Nitko nije otišo.

1552
00:46:14,940 --> 00:46:15,840
 Ostali smo.

1553
00:46:15,840 --> 00:46:17,680
 Nakon tri sekunde,

1554
00:46:17,680 --> 00:46:20,180
 taj Tenki odletio u zrak,

1555
00:46:20,180 --> 00:46:21,140
 pogodio ga je,

1556
00:46:21,140 --> 00:46:22,600
 baš pripadnik torbovoda,

1557
00:46:22,600 --> 00:46:23,560
 Miro Rodmanović,

1558
00:46:23,560 --> 00:46:25,060
 dobrovoljast,

1559
00:46:25,060 --> 00:46:25,920
 dečko iz policijac,

1560
00:46:25,920 --> 00:46:26,580
 iz preloga,

1561
00:46:26,580 --> 00:46:27,920
 ga je pogodio RPG-a,

1562
00:46:27,960 --> 00:46:28,900
 a mi to nismo znali.

1563
00:46:28,900 --> 00:46:30,660
 Miro je bio tamo u Jarku

1564
00:46:30,660 --> 00:46:32,400
 i vrebo je čekao i prigodnik.

1565
00:46:32,400 --> 00:46:33,000
 Mi nismo znali

1566
00:46:33,000 --> 00:46:33,860
 jel je Miro mrtav,

1567
00:46:33,860 --> 00:46:35,680
 jel je živ uopće,

1568
00:46:35,680 --> 00:46:37,140
 hoće li ga pogoditi,

1569
00:46:37,140 --> 00:46:38,000
 hoće li ga promašiti.

1570
00:46:38,000 --> 00:46:38,940
 To je vjerovatnost,

1571
00:46:38,940 --> 00:46:40,120
 veća da promaši nego da pogodi.

1572
00:46:40,120 --> 00:46:41,920
 A Tenki na 30 metra,

1573
00:46:41,920 --> 00:46:43,020
 znači treba još 5 sekundi,

1574
00:46:43,020 --> 00:46:43,640
 10 sekundi,

1575
00:46:43,640 --> 00:46:44,420
 i on je tu kodnosi

1576
00:46:44,420 --> 00:46:45,240
 i nas nema.

1577
00:46:45,240 --> 00:46:46,540
 Nitko nije otišo.

1578
00:46:46,540 --> 00:46:48,520
 Ako sto mladi mogu tada napraviti.

1579
00:46:48,520 --> 00:46:49,460
 Da, onda mogu i danas.

1580
00:46:49,460 --> 00:46:50,780
 Mogu i danas ove mladi napraviti.

1581
00:46:50,780 --> 00:46:52,400
 Ja često ono kako sam s djecom

1582
00:46:52,400 --> 00:46:55,220
 i čitala i gledala Tolkina,

1583
00:46:55,220 --> 00:46:58,180
 u gospodaru Prstenova,

1584
00:46:58,180 --> 00:46:59,920
 ta zadnja bitka koja se vodi,

1585
00:46:59,920 --> 00:47:02,860
 ta fiktivna bitka,

1586
00:47:02,860 --> 00:47:04,100
 ona me uvijek asocirana

1587
00:47:04,100 --> 00:47:06,260
 neki način na ove priče iz rata,

1588
00:47:06,260 --> 00:47:07,060
 na ove događaje,

1589
00:47:07,060 --> 00:47:07,940
 na ova svjedočanstva,

1590
00:47:07,940 --> 00:47:09,700
 jer tada se isto to događa.

1591
00:47:09,700 --> 00:47:12,080
 U stvari, oni idu uništiti prsten,

1592
00:47:12,080 --> 00:47:13,700
 oni ne znaju

1593
00:47:13,700 --> 00:47:15,080
 da li ga mogu uništiti,

1594
00:47:15,080 --> 00:47:16,480
 a istovremeno dolje ljudi

1595
00:47:16,480 --> 00:47:18,860
 idu u borbu protiv zla,

1596
00:47:18,860 --> 00:47:19,720
 okupljaju se.

1597
00:47:20,460 --> 00:47:21,260
 Isto ne znajući

1598
00:47:21,260 --> 00:47:22,980
 da li ovi uopće su još živi,

1599
00:47:22,980 --> 00:47:25,720
 da li to što oni rade

1600
00:47:25,720 --> 00:47:26,760
 će dati rezultat.

1601
00:47:26,760 --> 00:47:28,200
 A unatoči tome kažu

1602
00:47:28,200 --> 00:47:29,080
 ovo je naša bitka

1603
00:47:29,080 --> 00:47:30,320
 i mi ćemo joj voditi.

1604
00:47:30,320 --> 00:47:31,300
 Da, ja isto tako gledam

1605
00:47:31,300 --> 00:47:32,200
 i na ovo što je danas,

1606
00:47:32,200 --> 00:47:33,840
 u 21. u Hrvatskoj.

1607
00:47:33,840 --> 00:47:34,820
 Ovo je naša bitka.

1608
00:47:34,820 --> 00:47:36,680
 Ma mi Hrvati znamo voditi bitke.

1609
00:47:36,680 --> 00:47:37,660
 Uvijek smo znali u povijesti

1610
00:47:37,660 --> 00:47:38,440
 voditi bitke,

1611
00:47:38,440 --> 00:47:40,500
 ali izdobivene bitke

1612
00:47:40,500 --> 00:47:42,020
 uvijek umiruje prospemo.

1613
00:47:42,020 --> 00:47:43,560
 Evo, nikad nitko nije htio

1614
00:47:43,560 --> 00:47:45,140
 ni od novinara da si da truda

1615
00:47:45,140 --> 00:47:47,640
 i da ode u kod doktorice Bosanas,

1616
00:47:47,640 --> 00:47:48,040
 na primjer.

1617
00:47:48,040 --> 00:47:49,620
 Evo, to je novinarska tema,

1618
00:47:49,620 --> 00:47:50,260
 istraživačka,

1619
00:47:50,260 --> 00:47:51,180
 da je vrhunska.

1620
00:47:51,180 --> 00:47:53,060
 Da ode u kod doktorice Bosanas

1621
00:47:53,060 --> 00:47:53,840
 jer postoje papiri

1622
00:47:53,840 --> 00:47:54,920
 iz Vukovarske bolnice

1623
00:47:54,920 --> 00:47:55,480
 od ranjenika

1624
00:47:55,480 --> 00:47:56,380
 kad je ko zaprimljen,

1625
00:47:56,380 --> 00:47:57,060
 kad je ko ranjen.

1626
00:47:57,060 --> 00:47:58,740
 Da vidi koliko je srpskih vojnika

1627
00:47:58,740 --> 00:47:59,380
 zaprimljeno

1628
00:47:59,380 --> 00:48:00,780
 i koliko je srpskih vojnika

1629
00:48:00,780 --> 00:48:01,760
 predano na predaj

1630
00:48:01,760 --> 00:48:02,980
 i šlivančaninu u ruke.

1631
00:48:02,980 --> 00:48:03,940
 Ja mislim da je jedno

1632
00:48:03,940 --> 00:48:05,940
 8 do 10 srpskih vojnika

1633
00:48:05,940 --> 00:48:06,800
 i jedno narodne srvista

1634
00:48:06,800 --> 00:48:08,240
 lječeni, imali su posebnu sobu.

1635
00:48:08,240 --> 00:48:09,300
 Ja znam, dolazi su tamo,

1636
00:48:09,300 --> 00:48:10,180
 znam, vi su i bili.

1637
00:48:10,180 --> 00:48:11,720
 Znači, lječeni,

1638
00:48:11,720 --> 00:48:12,780
 po svim bovovim,

1639
00:48:12,780 --> 00:48:14,040
 predani njima.

1640
00:48:14,040 --> 00:48:16,520
 Ali to je izvor ponosa za nas,

1641
00:48:16,520 --> 00:48:17,340
 za ako narod.

1642
00:48:17,340 --> 00:48:17,720
 Upravo to.

1643
00:48:17,720 --> 00:48:18,780
 Ali željka, to ljudi ne znaju.

1644
00:48:18,780 --> 00:48:19,380
 Da, ne zna.

1645
00:48:19,380 --> 00:48:23,920
 S jedne strane,

1646
00:48:23,920 --> 00:48:25,280
 mi ih dovoljno ne naglašavamo,

1647
00:48:25,280 --> 00:48:25,820
 a s druge strane,

1648
00:48:25,820 --> 00:48:28,220
 ta stalna propaganda srpska

1649
00:48:28,220 --> 00:48:30,180
 laži o zločinima hrvatskim,

1650
00:48:30,180 --> 00:48:32,440
 priče koje oni stalno ponavljaju,

1651
00:48:32,440 --> 00:48:34,360
 optužujući sve na isti način

1652
00:48:34,360 --> 00:48:35,660
 za izolirane slučajeve,

1653
00:48:35,660 --> 00:48:36,680
 a s druge strane,

1654
00:48:36,680 --> 00:48:39,300
 ne govoreći o sistemskim zločinima

1655
00:48:39,300 --> 00:48:41,860
 srpskim koji su stalno se radili.

1656
00:48:41,860 --> 00:48:43,520
 Da, istina, slažem s tom,

1657
00:48:43,520 --> 00:48:44,900
 nedovoljno se zna o tom.

1658
00:48:44,900 --> 00:48:46,100
 Ali ti si, prosti,

1659
00:48:46,100 --> 00:48:48,400
 ti si za ovu

1660
00:48:48,400 --> 00:48:50,080
 obljetnicu, godišnicu,

1661
00:48:50,080 --> 00:48:52,840
 Vukovara si ispričao svoju

1662
00:48:52,840 --> 00:48:55,160
 jedno prezanimljivo svjedočanstvo.

1663
00:48:55,160 --> 00:48:56,440
 Aha, o zarobjeno moj.

1664
00:48:56,440 --> 00:48:57,900
 Da, da, da, da, ja sam da.

1665
00:48:57,900 --> 00:48:59,080
 Malo ti je, 55 minuta

1666
00:48:59,080 --> 00:49:00,480
 kad bi ja sam počeo pričati sve.

1667
00:49:00,480 --> 00:49:01,460
 Dobro.

1668
00:49:01,460 --> 00:49:02,300
 A to su, i to su pozitivno.

1669
00:49:02,300 --> 00:49:03,380
 Napravićemo drugi dio

1670
00:49:03,380 --> 00:49:04,940
 i treći dio, ali evo, daj.

1671
00:49:04,940 --> 00:49:06,700
 Da, u tome napadu

1672
00:49:06,700 --> 00:49:08,740
 14.9.15.16.17.

1673
00:49:08,740 --> 00:49:09,300
 To je četiri dana

1674
00:49:09,300 --> 00:49:10,500
 bio konstantan napad,

1675
00:49:10,500 --> 00:49:12,600
 taj tenkovski i pješadijski napad

1676
00:49:12,600 --> 00:49:13,320
 na trpinsku cestu

1677
00:49:13,320 --> 00:49:14,020
 i na sajmište.

1678
00:49:14,100 --> 00:49:15,160
 na dva mjesta se su udarali,

1679
00:49:15,160 --> 00:49:16,060
 niste nigde prošli.

1680
00:49:16,060 --> 00:49:18,060
 Pogođen je od tih silnih tenkova

1681
00:49:18,060 --> 00:49:18,700
 koji su tamo bili

1682
00:49:18,700 --> 00:49:19,740
 u njim stinkama što se vidi.

1683
00:49:19,740 --> 00:49:21,420
 Jedan tenk 84 je pogođen

1684
00:49:21,420 --> 00:49:23,800
 i kako to su novi tenkovi

1685
00:49:23,800 --> 00:49:25,020
 koji puste dimnu zavijesu.

1686
00:49:25,020 --> 00:49:25,980
 Puste dimnu zavijesu,

1687
00:49:25,980 --> 00:49:27,440
 tako da posada može izaći dolje

1688
00:49:27,440 --> 00:49:28,280
 i tako da ih ne vidiš

1689
00:49:28,280 --> 00:49:29,620
 da ih ne može se pogoditi.

1690
00:49:29,820 --> 00:49:30,760
 Jedan nam je se promakuo

1691
00:49:30,760 --> 00:49:33,240
 i saklio se u jednu poru

1692
00:49:33,240 --> 00:49:34,100
 u razlišenu kuću

1693
00:49:34,100 --> 00:49:36,020
 i oni se usklivo 10 dana.

1694
00:49:36,020 --> 00:49:37,040
 Nakon 10 dana

1695
00:49:37,040 --> 00:49:37,700
 smo nam preduše.

1696
00:49:37,700 --> 00:49:39,160
 Gladani bio.

1697
00:49:39,160 --> 00:49:39,640
 Gladani bio.

1698
00:49:39,640 --> 00:49:40,560
 Oni živeo i pradaji sosa

1699
00:49:40,560 --> 00:49:41,460
 žirive u šparizu,

1700
00:49:41,460 --> 00:49:42,100
 se saklivo,

1701
00:49:42,100 --> 00:49:43,740
 on je kod sebe imao škorpion,

1702
00:49:43,740 --> 00:49:45,080
 kao tenkisi što imaju,

1703
00:49:45,080 --> 00:49:46,140
 to ne pisto, škorpion.

1704
00:49:46,140 --> 00:49:47,900
 Znači u biti legitiman

1705
00:49:47,900 --> 00:49:50,500
 cilj u ratu,

1706
00:49:50,500 --> 00:49:51,520
 pogotovo u takvom ratu

1707
00:49:51,520 --> 00:49:52,680
 gdje si ti u okruženju

1708
00:49:52,680 --> 00:49:53,980
 da si ga upio,

1709
00:49:53,980 --> 00:49:54,720
 to ne bi bio,

1710
00:49:54,720 --> 00:49:55,380
 mislim ono,

1711
00:49:55,380 --> 00:49:56,480
 čovjek na tebe

1712
00:49:56,480 --> 00:49:57,580
 ti ga čekaš s puškom,

1713
00:49:57,580 --> 00:49:58,160
 mislim ono,

1714
00:49:58,160 --> 00:49:59,860
 total neravna pravna borba.

1715
00:49:59,860 --> 00:50:01,540
 Taj čovjek je odveden

1716
00:50:01,540 --> 00:50:02,860
 kod blage za razlištvo odveli.

1717
00:50:02,860 --> 00:50:03,900
 Kao ratni zarobljenik.

1718
00:50:03,900 --> 00:50:04,640
 Kao ratni zarobljenik,

1719
00:50:04,640 --> 00:50:05,680
 uzeli mu pištolj,

1720
00:50:05,680 --> 00:50:06,760
 odveli ga tamo,

1721
00:50:06,760 --> 00:50:07,980
 nikoga niti je maltretiruo,

1722
00:50:07,980 --> 00:50:08,600
 niti ga je tuko,

1723
00:50:08,600 --> 00:50:09,260
 niti ga je udario,

1724
00:50:09,260 --> 00:50:10,160
 niti mu čvoku udario,

1725
00:50:10,160 --> 00:50:10,620
 ništa.

1726
00:50:10,620 --> 00:50:11,540
 Odveli ga kod blage,

1727
00:50:11,540 --> 00:50:12,500
 zato je jedna veličina

1728
00:50:12,500 --> 00:50:13,340
 jednog čovjeka

1729
00:50:13,340 --> 00:50:14,300
 koji se rađa.

1730
00:50:14,300 --> 00:50:15,420
 Ja ga volim sprojiti

1731
00:50:15,420 --> 00:50:16,860
 sa blaženim kardinalnom

1732
00:50:16,860 --> 00:50:17,300
