1733
00:50:17,380 --> 00:50:18,100
 ako su dvije razlišta,

1734
00:50:18,100 --> 00:50:18,580
 ovaj je vojnik,

1735
00:50:18,580 --> 00:50:18,900
 ovaj je,

1736
00:50:18,900 --> 00:50:20,940
 ali u biti uvijek je ta je spona,

1737
00:50:20,940 --> 00:50:21,960
 srce,

1738
00:50:21,960 --> 00:50:23,440
 ljubav prema domovini,

1739
00:50:23,440 --> 00:50:24,700
 prema svom hrvatskom narodu

1740
00:50:24,700 --> 00:50:26,180
 je tu spojena u jednu.

1741
00:50:26,180 --> 00:50:27,180
 Da, kako ime ima,

1742
00:50:27,180 --> 00:50:27,800
