1743
00:50:27,800 --> 00:50:29,000
 fakat.

1744
00:50:29,000 --> 00:50:30,200
 Ali odmah čim je,

1745
00:50:30,200 --> 00:50:32,200
 čim je ta mjestna zajednica,

1746
00:50:32,200 --> 00:50:33,140
 gdje smo to stajali,

1747
00:50:33,140 --> 00:50:34,040
 gdje je i doveden,

1748
00:50:34,040 --> 00:50:34,560
 kasnije,

1749
00:50:34,560 --> 00:50:35,340
 stvarno doveden tamo

1750
00:50:35,340 --> 00:50:36,640
 preko puta u onom kafiću,

1751
00:50:36,640 --> 00:50:37,620
 ali gdje ta mjestna zajednica,

1752
00:50:37,620 --> 00:50:38,760
 bilo zvala se Bratstvo jedinstvo,

1753
00:50:39,100 --> 00:50:40,600
 blago zadraju odmah premijenovo

1754
00:50:40,600 --> 00:50:41,900
 od 90. godine

1755
00:50:41,900 --> 00:50:43,020
 u Alavizu je Stepinac,

1756
00:50:43,020 --> 00:50:44,040
 to stupno govori.

1757
00:50:44,040 --> 00:50:46,980
 Dobro, ali njemu ste dovali

1758
00:50:46,980 --> 00:50:47,880
 tog ratnog zarobljenika,

1759
00:50:47,880 --> 00:50:49,460
 koji je vozio tank na vas.

1760
00:50:49,460 --> 00:50:50,660
 Da, koji je zarobljen,

1761
00:50:50,660 --> 00:50:51,780
 koji je čovjek rezervista,

1762
00:50:51,780 --> 00:50:52,320
 ne redovan,

1763
00:50:52,320 --> 00:50:53,080
 vojnik rezervista.

1764
00:50:53,080 --> 00:50:54,520
 Dakle, on je bio mobiliziran

1765
00:50:54,520 --> 00:50:56,520
 u ratu u Zrbiji,

1766
00:50:56,520 --> 00:50:56,900
 dobro.

1767
00:50:56,900 --> 00:50:59,200
 I dovali ga prva riječ

1768
00:50:59,200 --> 00:51:00,300
 od blage,

1769
00:51:00,300 --> 00:51:01,680
 bilo mali je stig ladan.

1770
00:51:01,680 --> 00:51:03,080
 On je rekao,

1771
00:51:03,080 --> 00:51:03,580
 jesam,

1772
00:51:03,580 --> 00:51:04,620
 on mu je dao

1773
00:51:04,620 --> 00:51:05,800
 vrbovački narezak,

1774
00:51:05,800 --> 00:51:06,600
 točno se sjećam,

1775
00:51:09,100 --> 00:51:10,520
 i dok on to nije pojao,

1776
00:51:10,520 --> 00:51:11,700
 nikoga ništa nije pitao.

1777
00:51:11,700 --> 00:51:12,220
 Kad je pojao,

1778
00:51:12,220 --> 00:51:12,740
 onda ga je pitao,

1779
00:51:12,740 --> 00:51:13,920
 dakle si šta si onda rekao,

1780
00:51:13,920 --> 00:51:14,900
 iz Pančeva, ovo.

1781
00:51:14,900 --> 00:51:15,480
 Iz Pančeva,

1782
00:51:15,480 --> 00:51:16,260
 je došli iz Srbije.

1783
00:51:16,260 --> 00:51:17,000
 Da, da, ove.

1784
00:51:17,000 --> 00:51:17,780
 Sve.

1785
00:51:17,780 --> 00:51:19,960
 Taj čovjek danas živi

1786
00:51:19,960 --> 00:51:22,040
 u Hrvatskoj,

1787
00:51:22,040 --> 00:51:23,160
 u Zagrebu,

1788
00:51:23,160 --> 00:51:23,940
 taj čovjek se zove

1789
00:51:23,940 --> 00:51:24,780
 Siniša Jovanov,

1790
00:51:24,780 --> 00:51:26,040
 taj čovjek je moj prijatelj.

1791
00:51:26,040 --> 00:51:27,560
 Taj čovjek je prešao

1792
00:51:27,560 --> 00:51:28,620
 na hrvatsku stranu,

1793
00:51:28,620 --> 00:51:29,740
 kasnije je pogođen,

1794
00:51:29,740 --> 00:51:31,120
 o tome bi Amerika,

1795
00:51:31,120 --> 00:51:33,520
 cijeli sve bi znao

1796
00:51:33,520 --> 00:51:34,620
 za Sinišu Jovanova.

1797
00:51:34,620 --> 00:51:35,580
 Znači,

1798
00:51:35,580 --> 00:51:36,240
 zarobljen,

1799
00:51:36,240 --> 00:51:37,680
 kao srpski tenkista,

1800
00:51:37,680 --> 00:51:38,540
 prelazi,

1801
00:51:38,540 --> 00:51:39,780
 to može blago zadru,

1802
00:51:39,780 --> 00:51:41,720
 to može hrvatski branitelj,

1803
00:51:41,720 --> 00:51:42,560
 koji su se borili,

1804
00:51:42,560 --> 00:51:45,480
 ljubav od neprijateljskog vojnika,

1805
00:51:45,480 --> 00:51:46,620
 napraviti prijateljskog.

1806
00:51:46,620 --> 00:51:48,560
 Siniša Jovanov je kasnije ranjen

1807
00:51:48,560 --> 00:51:50,300
 u hrvatskom tenku,

1808
00:51:50,300 --> 00:51:51,380
 u T55,

1809
00:51:51,380 --> 00:51:52,480
 u Posavini,

1810
00:51:52,480 --> 00:51:54,580
 ranjen je u nogu,

1811
00:51:54,580 --> 00:51:55,340
 i ovo,

1812
00:51:55,340 --> 00:51:56,520
 ima hrvatsku mirovinu,

1813
00:51:56,520 --> 00:51:57,540
 živi u Zagrebu,

1814
00:51:57,540 --> 00:51:58,640
 i, ovo,

1815
00:51:58,640 --> 00:51:59,140
 prijatelji.

1816
00:51:59,140 --> 00:52:00,140
 I mi smo prijatelji.

1817
00:52:00,140 --> 00:52:00,420
 Da,

1818
00:52:00,420 --> 00:52:01,580
 kako je moguće.

1819
00:52:01,580 --> 00:52:02,880
 Jel to zanima Milora Pupovica,

1820
00:52:02,880 --> 00:52:03,400
 ta priča?

1821
00:52:03,400 --> 00:52:03,920
 Ne, ne, ne.

1822
00:52:03,920 --> 00:52:04,980
 Jel zanima priča,

1823
00:52:04,980 --> 00:52:06,120
 ovo nisam nikad ispričao,

1824
00:52:06,120 --> 00:52:07,260
 u Bosanskom odvojku,

1825
00:52:07,260 --> 00:52:07,840
 pa,

1826
00:52:07,840 --> 00:52:09,320
 sedam dana prije pada,

1827
00:52:09,320 --> 00:52:11,180
 već su nam presjekli komunikaciju

1828
00:52:11,180 --> 00:52:12,780
 između Borova naselja i Zbukovara.

1829
00:52:12,780 --> 00:52:14,380
 Mi smo se borili jedno deset dana,

1830
00:52:14,380 --> 00:52:15,480
 i više,

1831
00:52:15,480 --> 00:52:17,220
 jedno četrnaest dana smo se borili

1832
00:52:17,220 --> 00:52:18,380
 bez bolnice,

1833
00:52:18,380 --> 00:52:19,680
 bez doktora Njavre,

1834
00:52:19,680 --> 00:52:20,320
 koji su radili

1835
00:52:20,320 --> 00:52:22,720
 u katastrofalno užasnim uvjetima.

1836
00:52:28,640 --> 00:52:30,000
 nije mi više moglo spojiti.

1837
00:52:30,000 --> 00:52:31,520
 I u Bosanskom odvoji,

1838
00:52:31,520 --> 00:52:32,240
 ko su nam ušli,

1839
00:52:32,240 --> 00:52:33,040
 to je bilo...

1840
00:52:33,040 --> 00:52:34,220
 Bosanski odvojak je,

1841
00:52:34,220 --> 00:52:34,620
 što?

1842
00:52:34,620 --> 00:52:36,140
 Ulica je jedna u Bosanskoj,

1843
00:52:36,140 --> 00:52:37,220
 tu je blagozada stanovo,

1844
00:52:37,220 --> 00:52:37,920
 tu je njegova kuća,

1845
00:52:37,920 --> 00:52:39,420
 od Bosanska 11.

1846
00:52:39,420 --> 00:52:40,580
 E, odmah,

1847
00:52:40,580 --> 00:52:42,240
 od njegove kuće ima mala vakuličica,

1848
00:52:42,240 --> 00:52:44,360
 slijepa Bosanski odvojak.

1849
00:52:44,360 --> 00:52:45,200
 Tu su nam ušli,

1850
00:52:45,200 --> 00:52:46,380
 i to je već bio problem.

1851
00:52:46,380 --> 00:52:46,920
 Došli su nam,

1852
00:52:46,920 --> 00:52:48,400
 znači, na 30 metara.

1853
00:52:48,400 --> 00:52:50,960
 Tu je bilo neprekidna borba,

1854
00:52:50,960 --> 00:52:51,660
 prsa u prsa,

1855
00:52:51,660 --> 00:52:53,040
 ono bukvalno kuća za kuću,

1856
00:52:53,040 --> 00:52:53,520
 i,

1857
00:52:53,520 --> 00:52:54,960
 pogodimo,

1858
00:52:54,960 --> 00:52:56,320
 jednog njihova htio je pretrčat,

1859
00:52:56,320 --> 00:52:57,000
 pogodimo ga,

1860
00:52:57,000 --> 00:52:59,540
 meta ga je štrajfovo,

1861
00:52:59,540 --> 00:53:00,780
 pao je na sve ceste,

1862
00:53:00,780 --> 00:53:01,980
 on je urliko,

1863
00:53:01,980 --> 00:53:02,620
 cičio,

1864
00:53:02,620 --> 00:53:02,980
 i ovo,

1865
00:53:02,980 --> 00:53:04,280
 mi smo prestali pucat,

1866
00:53:04,280 --> 00:53:05,080
 mogli smo ga ubiti,

1867
00:53:05,080 --> 00:53:06,500
 od 30 metara mogli smo pucati od njega,

1868
00:53:06,500 --> 00:53:07,060
 ali ranjen je,

1869
00:53:07,060 --> 00:53:08,120
 u ranjenika su više ne pucati,

1870
00:53:08,120 --> 00:53:08,640
 gotovo,

1871
00:53:08,640 --> 00:53:10,180
 k'on smeta više ranjen čovjeka,

1872
00:53:10,180 --> 00:53:11,020
 izbačen je stroja.

1873
00:53:11,020 --> 00:53:11,900
 Mi njima,

1874
00:53:11,900 --> 00:53:13,800
 dovikujemo se sa njima ženjika,

1875
00:53:13,800 --> 00:53:15,300
 sa nepreteskim vojnicima se dovikujemo.

1876
00:53:15,300 --> 00:53:16,040
 Mi kažemo,

1877
00:53:16,040 --> 00:53:16,860
 nećemo pucat,

1878
00:53:16,980 --> 00:53:17,720
 idite po njega,

1879
00:53:17,720 --> 00:53:18,480
 idite po njega,

1880
00:53:18,480 --> 00:53:19,140
 izvucite ga,

1881
00:53:19,140 --> 00:53:19,420
 idite ga,

1882
00:53:19,420 --> 00:53:19,580
 doma,

1883
00:53:19,580 --> 00:53:20,260
 spašavajte ga.

1884
00:53:20,260 --> 00:53:22,380
 Nakon pol minute dolazi,

1885
00:53:22,380 --> 00:53:23,380
 predstavljaju se oni pucat,

1886
00:53:23,380 --> 00:53:24,740
 sad ostalo je muk,

1887
00:53:24,740 --> 00:53:26,140
 iz jedne i druge strane niko ne puca,

1888
00:53:26,140 --> 00:53:27,100
 ovaj je samo jaučan,

1889
00:53:27,100 --> 00:53:27,960
 na sve ceste.

1890
00:53:27,960 --> 00:53:30,960
 Nakon pola minuta dolazi odgovor,

1891
00:53:30,960 --> 00:53:31,260
 kaže,

1892
00:53:31,260 --> 00:53:31,860
 ne,

1893
00:53:31,860 --> 00:53:33,080
 mi nećemo pucat,

1894
00:53:33,080 --> 00:53:33,940
 idite vi po njega,

1895
00:53:33,940 --> 00:53:34,920
 mi po njihovo.

1896
00:53:34,920 --> 00:53:36,920
 I dvojice naše idu,

1897
00:53:36,920 --> 00:53:37,540
 naša dvojica,

1898
00:53:37,540 --> 00:53:39,320
 mi ih štitimo,

1899
00:53:39,320 --> 00:53:41,160
 naša dvojica dečki istrče,

1900
00:53:41,320 --> 00:53:42,020
 postave puške,

1901
00:53:42,020 --> 00:53:43,080
 isto će potpuniti,

1902
00:53:43,080 --> 00:53:44,040
 uhvate njega,

1903
00:53:44,040 --> 00:53:44,900
 dovuku ga,

1904
00:53:44,900 --> 00:53:45,760
 do nas.

1905
00:53:45,760 --> 00:53:47,200
 Ja sjećam,

1906
00:53:47,200 --> 00:53:48,300
 ja sam pitao da kve si,

1907
00:53:48,300 --> 00:53:49,760
 prvo pitao da kve si.

1908
00:53:49,760 --> 00:53:51,000
 Kaže on iz Niša,

1909
00:53:51,000 --> 00:53:52,440
 pa ja kažem što radiš ovdje,

1910
00:53:52,440 --> 00:53:53,860
 što si došao u Vukovar,

1911
00:53:53,860 --> 00:53:55,360
 u Hrvatsku.

1912
00:53:55,360 --> 00:53:56,040
 Da, u Hrvatsku.

1913
00:53:56,040 --> 00:53:56,680
 Kaže,

1914
00:53:56,680 --> 00:53:58,240
 došao sam osvetit prijatelja,

1915
00:53:58,240 --> 00:53:59,600
 poginio je prije 15 dana u Vukovar,

1916
00:53:59,600 --> 00:54:00,360
 došao je on osvetit.

1917
00:54:00,360 --> 00:54:01,300
 A drži,

1918
00:54:01,300 --> 00:54:01,900
 šta je on radio,

1919
00:54:01,900 --> 00:54:03,520
 šta je njegov prijatelj radio

1920
00:54:03,520 --> 00:54:04,940
 u Vukovar istom,

1921
00:54:04,940 --> 00:54:05,660
 iz Niša.

1922
00:54:05,660 --> 00:54:07,080
 Čovjek šesto kilometara od Vukovar.

1923
00:54:07,080 --> 00:54:07,320
 Naravno.

1924
00:54:07,320 --> 00:54:08,920
 I drži crjeva u ruci.

1925
00:54:08,920 --> 00:54:09,740
 Crjeva,

1926
00:54:09,740 --> 00:54:10,880
 štrafo ga je metak,

1927
00:54:10,880 --> 00:54:11,880
 njemu su crjeva ispala

1928
00:54:11,880 --> 00:54:13,140
 iz utrobe.

1929
00:54:13,140 --> 00:54:15,240
 Odvedan je u Borovo komerc,

1930
00:54:15,240 --> 00:54:16,540
 tamo je predan,

1931
00:54:16,540 --> 00:54:18,500
 bilo je jedan liječnik opće prakse

1932
00:54:18,500 --> 00:54:19,860
 i dvije medijenske sestre.

1933
00:54:19,860 --> 00:54:21,680
 Nažalost je čovjek umro

1934
00:54:21,680 --> 00:54:22,480
 nakon četve dana.

1935
00:54:22,480 --> 00:54:24,360
 Da su ga oni odvezli,

1936
00:54:24,360 --> 00:54:26,380
 oni su imali bolnicu,

1937
00:54:26,380 --> 00:54:27,320
 ta čovjek je preživio.

1938
00:54:27,320 --> 00:54:29,420
 Oni su Boga nisu htjeli uzeti,

1939
00:54:29,420 --> 00:54:30,480
 mi smo ga uzeli,

1940
00:54:30,480 --> 00:54:32,960
 odveli ga u Borovo komerc,

1941
00:54:33,340 --> 00:54:34,540
 nažalost je preminuo, da.

1942
00:54:34,540 --> 00:54:37,100
 To je ovo što kažeš,

1943
00:54:37,100 --> 00:54:38,480
 te priče,

1944
00:54:38,480 --> 00:54:40,520
 te istinita svjedočanstva,

1945
00:54:40,520 --> 00:54:41,720
 ti događaj nevjerojatni,

1946
00:54:41,720 --> 00:54:44,580
 koliko se malo napravilo

1947
00:54:44,580 --> 00:54:46,260
 i filmska industrija u Hrvatskoj,

1948
00:54:46,260 --> 00:54:47,340
 gotovo ništa.

1949
00:54:47,340 --> 00:54:48,400
 Za Svi Niša Jovanova,

1950
00:54:48,400 --> 00:54:49,780
 da to je to priča,

1951
00:54:49,780 --> 00:54:50,900
 koliko čijeli svijet bi znao,

1952
00:54:50,900 --> 00:54:53,200
 čovjek bi bilo.

1953
00:54:53,200 --> 00:54:55,280
 Ali on potvrđuje istinu

1954
00:54:55,280 --> 00:54:56,220
 u domovinskom ratu,

1955
00:54:56,220 --> 00:54:57,340
 a to se ne zna.

1956
00:54:57,340 --> 00:54:57,900
 A to se ne zna.

1957
00:54:57,900 --> 00:54:59,280
 Ali dobro, sad,

1958
00:54:59,280 --> 00:55:00,760
 tvoji planovi sada,

1959
00:55:00,760 --> 00:55:02,360
 evo, u budućnosti,

1960
00:55:02,940 --> 00:55:04,120
 u ovi sljedeći koraci,

1961
00:55:04,120 --> 00:55:05,880
 skoro dolaze lokalni izbori,

1962
00:55:05,880 --> 00:55:07,900
 ti si ušao kao zastupnik

1963
00:55:07,900 --> 00:55:09,440
 iz četvrte izborne jedinice.

1964
00:55:09,440 --> 00:55:10,480
 Dakle, što,

1965
00:55:10,480 --> 00:55:12,920
 koji su planovi tvoji stipo?

1966
00:55:12,920 --> 00:55:15,920
 Što ti želiš sad još ostvariti za Hrvatsku?

1967
00:55:16,100 --> 00:55:17,800
 Pa želim ostvariti sad,

1968
00:55:17,800 --> 00:55:19,180
 evo, baš na lokalnim izborima,

1969
00:55:19,180 --> 00:55:21,020
 to me je fasciniralo u kampanji,

1970
00:55:21,020 --> 00:55:22,300
 bio sam u četvrtoj izbornoj jedinici,

1971
00:55:22,300 --> 00:55:23,780
 inače sam predsjednik

1972
00:55:23,780 --> 00:55:25,820
 županijskog ogranka,

1973
00:55:25,820 --> 00:55:26,600
 domovinskog pokljeda,

1974
00:55:26,600 --> 00:55:28,340
 županije u Vukovatsko-Sijemske,

1975
00:55:28,340 --> 00:55:29,920
 sad sam došao baš na svoj teritorij,

1976
00:55:29,920 --> 00:55:30,660
 nisam se borio.

1977
00:55:30,720 --> 00:55:31,040
 Pa da.

1978
00:55:31,040 --> 00:55:34,520
 Želim objasniti ljudima,

1979
00:55:34,520 --> 00:55:36,580
 pogotovo na selima Šeljke,

1980
00:55:36,580 --> 00:55:38,400
 želim im objasniti

1981
00:55:38,400 --> 00:55:39,940
 da Franjo Tuđman više nije živ,

1982
00:55:39,940 --> 00:55:41,700
 da ovo nije onaj HDZ

1983
00:55:41,700 --> 00:55:43,120
 za koji su oni gledali,

1984
00:55:43,120 --> 00:55:44,340
 jer ljudi još misle,

1985
00:55:44,340 --> 00:55:45,680
 jes to doživio u kampanji?

1986
00:55:45,680 --> 00:55:47,420
 Gdje HDZ pobjeđuje?

1987
00:55:47,420 --> 00:55:48,940
 Pa pobjeđuje u Županiji

1988
00:55:48,940 --> 00:55:50,660
 u Osječko-Baranjskoj,

1989
00:55:50,660 --> 00:55:51,280
 u Anušići.

1990
00:55:51,280 --> 00:55:51,400
 Da.

1991
00:55:51,400 --> 00:55:52,940
 I pobjeđuje u prvom krugu.

1992
00:55:52,940 --> 00:55:53,620
 Karikira.

1993
00:55:53,620 --> 00:55:55,200
 Zašto? U Županiji.

1994
00:55:55,200 --> 00:55:56,820
 A u Osječku nisu bili nikad na vlasti.

1995
00:55:57,500 --> 00:55:58,540
 To te sve govori.

1996
00:55:58,540 --> 00:55:58,800
 Da.

1997
00:55:58,800 --> 00:56:00,340
 U maso tako.

1998
00:56:00,340 --> 00:56:01,600
 Znači to rula.

1999
00:56:01,600 --> 00:56:03,860
 A doživio sam u kampanji

2000
00:56:03,860 --> 00:56:04,880
 gdje mi izađu

2001
00:56:04,880 --> 00:56:07,400
 stariji van

2002
00:56:07,400 --> 00:56:09,520
 plaćući, kažu imam tri,

2003
00:56:09,520 --> 00:56:11,900
 dva sina, jednu čer,

2004
00:56:11,900 --> 00:56:12,980
 šester unučadi,

2005
00:56:12,980 --> 00:56:13,740
 ovi u Irskoj,

2006
00:56:13,740 --> 00:56:14,040
 ovi u njima.

2007
00:56:14,040 --> 00:56:15,380
 Niko nema, oni sami.

2008
00:56:15,380 --> 00:56:16,220
 Strašno.

2009
00:56:16,220 --> 00:56:17,460
 I glasaju i dalje

2010
00:56:17,460 --> 00:56:18,740
 za onoga koji ih je potjero.

2011
00:56:18,740 --> 00:56:20,180
 Koji su ispraznili

2012
00:56:20,180 --> 00:56:21,560
 hrvatske teritorije,

2013
00:56:21,560 --> 00:56:23,220
 koji su obranjeni.

2014
00:56:23,220 --> 00:56:25,000
 Dakle, ono što je obranjeno

2015
00:56:25,000 --> 00:56:26,160
 u ratu sada u miru

2016
00:56:26,160 --> 00:56:27,620
 se prazni od Hrvata.

2017
00:56:27,620 --> 00:56:28,840
 I što bi volio još jedno

2018
00:56:28,840 --> 00:56:29,580
 za poruku,

2019
00:56:29,580 --> 00:56:31,220
 to bi volio osvijestiti

2020
00:56:31,220 --> 00:56:32,200
 i volio bi osvijestiti

2021
00:56:32,200 --> 00:56:33,380
 kod hrvatskih branitelja

2022
00:56:33,380 --> 00:56:34,220
 da ne,

2023
00:56:34,220 --> 00:56:35,800
 to sam milijardu puta čuo,

2024
00:56:35,800 --> 00:56:37,160
 vjerovatno si ti to čula,

2025
00:56:37,160 --> 00:56:39,000
 dali su nam je rovinu.

2026
00:56:39,080 --> 00:56:40,820
 Nitko nam ništa nije dao.

2027
00:56:40,820 --> 00:56:42,640
 Nitko nam ništa nije.

2028
00:56:42,640 --> 00:56:43,440
 Mi smo njima dali.

2029
00:56:43,440 --> 00:56:43,900
 Tako je.

2030
00:56:43,900 --> 00:56:45,520
 Pozicije, fotelje,

2031
00:56:45,520 --> 00:56:47,540
 ali nažalost ne rade kako treba.

2032
00:56:47,540 --> 00:56:49,420
 I za još jednu emisiju

2033
00:56:49,420 --> 00:56:50,300
 bi bio razgovor uopće

2034
00:56:50,300 --> 00:56:51,760
 o tom načinu na koji se,

2035
00:56:51,760 --> 00:56:52,420
 nažalost,

2036
00:56:52,420 --> 00:56:54,040
 najsposobnije među nama,

2037
00:56:54,040 --> 00:56:55,160
 među braniteljima,

2038
00:56:55,160 --> 00:56:56,360
 najpoduzetnije na kraju

2039
00:56:56,360 --> 00:56:58,180
 tjeralo da idu u mirovinu

2040
00:56:58,180 --> 00:57:00,040
 umjesto da ih se u stvari poticalo

2041
00:57:00,040 --> 00:57:01,300
 da dalje ostanu aktivni

2042
00:57:01,300 --> 00:57:02,220
 u hrvatskom društvu.

2043
00:57:02,220 --> 00:57:03,760
 Ali baš se to nije željelo.

2044
00:57:03,860 --> 00:57:04,900
 Ali to se baš nije.

2045
00:57:04,900 --> 00:57:06,360
 Ko što se snije naša dijaspora?

2046
00:57:06,360 --> 00:57:07,060
 Tako je.

2047
00:57:07,060 --> 00:57:08,420
 Ne može se vratiti u Hrvatsku.

2048
00:57:08,420 --> 00:57:09,760
 Ne može se vratiti u Hrvatsku nikako.

2049
00:57:09,760 --> 00:57:10,440
 Ljudi žele doći.

2050
00:57:10,440 --> 00:57:10,900
 Ne mogu, kaže,

2051
00:57:10,900 --> 00:57:12,520
 dobiti građevinsku dozbu za roditeljsku kuću

2052
00:57:12,520 --> 00:57:13,340
 da obnovim,

2053
00:57:13,340 --> 00:57:14,260
 a kamo da radim posao,

2054
00:57:14,260 --> 00:57:14,780
 kaže ozbiljno.

2055
00:57:14,780 --> 00:57:15,920
 Kaže, pa svi me traži odmah novice,

2056
00:57:15,920 --> 00:57:16,940
 kaže, pa ne pade me na pamet.

2057
00:57:16,940 --> 00:57:18,140
 Dobro, Slipo, mislim,

2058
00:57:18,140 --> 00:57:19,460
 sad si, evo,

2059
00:57:19,460 --> 00:57:20,780
 puno te posla čeka

2060
00:57:20,780 --> 00:57:22,460
 u Hrvatskom saboru,

2061
00:57:22,460 --> 00:57:23,220
 u politici,

2062
00:57:23,380 --> 00:57:26,080
 jedino što mogu reći,

2063
00:57:26,080 --> 00:57:27,760
 nikad u životu

2064
00:57:27,760 --> 00:57:29,060
 neću ići ispod jedne crte

2065
00:57:29,060 --> 00:57:30,360
 koju ja imam u životu.

2066
00:57:30,360 --> 00:57:32,200
 A to je poštenje,

2067
00:57:32,200 --> 00:57:33,780
 čast, domoljublje,

2068
00:57:33,780 --> 00:57:34,380
 vjera,

2069
00:57:34,380 --> 00:57:35,740
 evo, ta crta se ne prelazi.

2070
00:57:35,740 --> 00:57:38,120
 To kad bi prešo,

2071
00:57:38,120 --> 00:57:40,580
 pljunio bi na sve poginule svoje prijatelje,

2072
00:57:40,580 --> 00:57:42,060
 pljunio bi na svog brata,

2073
00:57:42,060 --> 00:57:43,840
 pljunio bi na svog pokojnog oca,

2074
00:57:43,840 --> 00:57:45,140
 majku i na sve svoje.

2075
00:57:45,140 --> 00:57:47,180
 I na svoju ženu i dvoje djeca,

2076
00:57:47,180 --> 00:57:47,680
 dva sina.

2077
00:57:47,680 --> 00:57:49,360
 Nikad to neću preći.

2078
00:57:50,240 --> 00:57:51,600
 I neće se zameniti nikad čutko

2079
00:57:51,600 --> 00:57:53,560
 svaki dan što se HDZ otvore za župan,

2080
00:57:53,560 --> 00:57:54,380
 da neko dobio mito,

2081
00:57:54,380 --> 00:57:56,000
 da sam dobio to prvi put

2082
00:57:56,000 --> 00:57:56,660
 kad bih napravio,

2083
00:57:56,660 --> 00:57:57,760
 ja bradi u Dunavskoći.

2084
00:57:57,760 --> 00:58:00,100
 Dobro, neće biti potrebe.

2085
00:58:00,100 --> 00:58:01,200
 Hvala ti puno.

2086
00:58:01,200 --> 00:58:02,300
 Vama zahvaljujem,

2087
00:58:02,300 --> 00:58:03,160
 gledatelji,

2088
00:58:03,160 --> 00:58:04,960
 na vremenu koje ste odvojili

2089
00:58:04,960 --> 00:58:07,120
 da sastušate današnji naš razgovor

2090
00:58:07,120 --> 00:58:09,160
 i pozdravljam vas do sljedećeg prilike.

2091
00:58:20,240 --> 00:58:38,260
 Hvala ti puno.

